  ('IntexGlobal','5022','Alphard 5 Panel Nylon Foam Trucker Cap','alphard-5-panel-nylon-foam-trucker-cap-5022','Headwear','Caps','<p class="" data-start="185" data-end="491">Introducing the Alphard 5 Panel Nylon Foam Trucker Cap, designed with breathable mesh sides and lightweight foam front for all-day comfort. Crafted for casual wear, events, or promotions, it features a classic trucker style with a structured front panel and adjustable snapback closure for the perfect fit.</p>',25,true,false,'["Fabric/Material: Foam Front with Nylon Mesh Side and Back Panels.", "Visor: Pre-curved Visor with Matching Undervisor."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Closure", "value": "Adjustable Plastic Snapback."}, {"name": "Profile", "value": "High Profile."}, {"name": "Panels", "value": "5 Panels."}, {"name": "Structured", "value": "Yes (Foam Structured Front)."}, {"name": "Back", "value": "Mesh Back for Ventilation."}, {"name": "Eyelets", "value": "None (Breathable Mesh)."}, {"name": "Size", "value": "One Size Fits All."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black & White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5022/5022-black-white.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5022/5022-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy & White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5022/5022-navy-white.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5022/5022-navy.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5022/5022-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/alphard/');
