  ('IntexGlobal','5101','Colorado Backpack Tote Bag','colorado-backpack-tote-bag-5101','Bags','Tote Bags','The Colorado Backpack is designed for those who demand practicality, durability, and eco-consciousness in their gear. Whether navigating the urban jungle or exploring the great outdoors, this 45-litre backpack has you covered.',10,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Construction: Made from recycled materials, supporting sustainability.", "Spacious 45L Capacity: Ideal for carrying all your essentials for work, travel, or outdoor activities.", "Integrated Rain Cover: Provides reliable protection against unexpected weather.", "Secure Laptop Storage: Padded compartment fits laptops up to 16” with a suspended cradle for added protection.", "Tablet Slot and Soft-Lined Pocket: Dedicated spaces for tablets, phones, or sunglasses.", "Smart Organization: Multi-compartment design includes a built-in organizer with storage pouches, pen holders, zippered pocket, and key clip.", "Travel-Friendly Features: Equipped with a travel sleeve and a concealed RFID protection pocket for security on the go.", "Quick-Access Hip Pocket: Convenient storage for small items like snacks or keys.", "Safety Features: Reflective trim enhances visibility in low light conditions.", "Side Bottle Pocket: Holds bottles or beverages for hydration on the move.", "Water-Resistant Fabric: Built to withstand various weather conditions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm W x 53cm H x 28cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5101/5101-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/colorado-backpack/');
