  ('IntexGlobal','5102','Fitzroy Backpack Tote Bag','fitzroy-backpack-tote-bag-5102','Bags','Tote Bags','The Fitzroy Backpack is the ideal companion for professionals and adventurers seeking functionality, style, and reliability. With a 34-litre capacity and smart organizational features, this backpack is designed to keep you comfortable and prepared, wherever your day takes you.',10,true,false,'["Padded Laptop Sleeve: Fits laptops up to 17 inches, accessible through an easy-to-reach back zipper.", "Organizer Compartment: Includes multiple pockets, a zippered mesh pocket, and a built-in key fob for convenient storage.", "Media Player Pocket: Secure and accessible compartment for your gadgets.", "Valuables Pocket: Dedicated space for smartphones or other small essentials.", "Side Mesh Water Bottle Pocket: Keeps hydration within easy reach.", "Ergonomic Shoulder Straps: S-shaped mesh shoulder straps with padding, a suspension system, thumb-ring pulls, and a cell phone pocket for ultimate comfort and utility.", "Mesh Grab Handle: Durable and comfortable for quick carrying.", "Padded Back Panel: Provides superior comfort and support, with a tuck-away waist belt for added stability when needed.", "Spacious Main Compartment: Offers approximately 34 litres of capacity, perfect for work, travel, or outdoor adventures."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "33cm(w) x 48cm(h) x 21.9cm(d)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5102/5102-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/fitzroy-backpack/');
