  ('IntexGlobal','5103','Eiger Backpack Tote Bag','eiger-backpack-tote-bag-5103','Bags','Tote Bags','The Eiger Backpack is the ultimate companion for travelers, commuters, and students who value efficiency and convenience. With its checkpoint-friendly features and robust design, this 42-litre backpack ensures you stay organized and ready for any adventure.',10,true,false,'["Durable Material: Made from rugged 600D PolyCanvas for enhanced durability and long-lasting use.", "Spacious Design: Offers four compartments for easy organization and ample storage space.", "Checkpoint-Friendly Layout: Designed to simplify airport security checks, making travel hassle-free.", "Padded Laptop Compartment: Fits laptops up to 17 inches with extra cushioning for protection.", "Dedicated Tablet Sleeve: A secure space for iPads or other tablets.", "Organizer Section: Includes a mesh pocket, pen holders, and a built-in key clip to keep essentials in place.", "Side Water Bottle Pocket: Convenient access to hydration while on the go.", "Generous Capacity: Main compartment provides approximately 42 litres of storage, perfect for work, travel, or school."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "41cm(w) x 54cm(h) x 23cm(d)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5103/5103-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/eiger-backpack/');
