  ('IntexGlobal','5105','Fairweather Backpack Tote Bag','fairweather-backpack-tote-bag-5105','Bags','Tote Bags','The Fairweather Backpack offers a perfect blend of simplicity, sustainability, and functionality for professionals who value efficiency and style. Designed with recycled materials, this sleek and compact backpack is ideal for everyday use.',10,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Materials: Made from recycled poly fabric crafted from repurposed plastic bottles, combining sustainability with water resistance and durability.", "Dedicated Laptop Compartment: Cushioned compartment fits laptops up to 15.6 inches, featuring an adjustable sling system to keep your device secure during travel.", "Compact Design: Lightweight at just 0.45 kg, with dimensions of 44 cm x 31 cm x 13 cm and a 17L capacity, perfect for carrying essentials.", "Multiple Compartments: Includes a main compartment for books or larger items, a digital compartment for tablets and gadgets, and an easy-access side pocket for umbrellas or water bottles.", "Comfortable Carrying: Ergonomically padded shoulder straps and a soft microfiber handle ensure all-day comfort.", "Sleek Features: Includes webbing puller zippers for smooth, quick access and a minimalist logo detail for a professional look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "44cm H x 31cm L x 13cm W"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/5105/5105-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/fairweather-backpack/');
