  ('IntexGlobal','ASSN01','Hacky Sack Outdoor Toy','hacky-sack-outdoor-toy-assn01','Toys & Games','Outdoor Toys','The Hacky Sack is a lightweight and engaging promotional item, perfect for sports enthusiasts, outdoor events, and corporate giveaways. Filled with plastic granules, this compact and portable footbag offers hours of entertainment while keeping your brand in focus.',250,true,false,'["Durable Construction: Designed for long-lasting use in recreational play.", "Plastic Granule Filling: Provides a balanced weight for controlled kicks and tricks.", "Compact & Portable: Fits easily in pockets or bags for on-the-go fun.", "Great for All Ages: Ideal for casual play, team-building activities, and outdoor fun.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-purple.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-red.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn01/assn01-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'su