  ('IntexGlobal','ASSN10','Printed Shoelaces Apparel Accessory','printed-shoelaces-apparel-accessory-assn10','Apparel','Apparel Accessories','The Printed Shoelaces are a fun and cost-effective promotional giveaway, ideal for sports events, fitness brands, and lifestyle promotions. These customizable shoelaces provide a unique branding opportunity while offering a practical and stylish accessory for sneakers, athletic shoes, and casual footwear.',250,true,false,'["Durable & High-Quality Material: Designed for everyday wear and long-lasting use.", "Customizable Branding: Can be printed with logos or designs for maximum visibility.", "Versatile & Stylish: Suitable for sports, casual wear, and fashion accessories.", "Low-Cost Promotional Giveaway: A budget-friendly marketing tool for mass distribution.", "Great for Sports & Fitness Promotions: Ideal for marathons, gyms, schools, and team events."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "1 (w) x 90 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Baby Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-baby-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Baby Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-baby-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-black.webp"}, {"name": "Brown", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-brown.webp"}, {"name": "Burgundy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-burgundy.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/assn10/assn10-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "http