  ('IntexGlobal','AUTO21','Astro Side Window Car Sunshade Car Accessory','astro-side-window-car-sunshade-car-accessory-auto21','Tools & Auto','Car Accessories','The Side Window Car Sunshade is a practical and effective accessory designed to reduce glare, block UV rays, and keep car interiors cooler. Featuring PVC suction cups for a secure hold, this lightweight and foldable sunshade is easy to install, remove, and store, making it a great promotional giveaway for car owners.',250,true,false,'["UV Protection & Heat Reduction: Helps shield passengers from sun exposure.", "Durable & Lightweight Material: Made for long-lasting use.", "Foldable & Portable Design: Easily folds for convenient storage.", "Easy Installation: Secures to windows with strong PVC suction cups.", "Universal Fit: Suitable for most vehicle side windows.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36 (w) x 47 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/auto21/auto21-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.42,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/side-window-car-sunshade/');
