  ('IntexGlobal','BB5001','500ml Bell Bottle with Carry Handle','500ml-bell-bottle-with-carry-handle-bb5001','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing the 500ml Bell Bottle with Carry Handle, featuring a modern design and practical functionality. Available in six vibrant colours, this premium vacuum-insulated bottle ensures your drinks stay cold for longer, while offering easy portability with its carry handle and fold-out silicone sipper.',50,true,false,'["Available in 8 Colours: Choose from Red, Yellow, Black, Cream, Baby Blue, Navy, Grey and Lilac, each with a solid powder-coated finish for a sleek, modern look.", "500ml Vacuum Bottle: Keeps your drinks cold for longer with double-walled insulation.", "Stylish Carry Handle & Silicone Sipper: The lid features a convenient carry handle and a fold-out silicone sipper for easy sipping.", "Premium 304 Stainless Steel: Durable stainless steel inner and outer layers, with a copper-plated lining for superior insulation.", "100% Leakproof & Puncture/Rust Resistant: Built to withstand everyday wear and tear.", "Customizable: Perfect for laser engraving or printing, ideal for promotional items or personalized gifts.", "Dishwasher Safe: Easy to clean (exclusive of decoration).", "Not Suitable for Hot or Carbonated Beverages or Food: Best used with cold drinks.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in an eco-friendly BELL branded carton."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "23.5 x 7.5 cm diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Baby Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5001/bb5001-baby-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5001/bb5001-black.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5001/bb5001-cream.webp"}, {"name": "Lilac"