  ('IntexGlobal','BB5002','500ml Bell Bottle with Infuser Lid','500ml-bell-bottle-with-infuser-lid-bb5002','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing the 500ml Bell Bottle with Infuser Lid, designed to infuse your favourite fruits, herbs, or teas for a refreshing twist.',50,true,false,'["Available in 8 Colours: Choose from Red, Yellow, Black, Cream, Baby Blue, Navy, Grey and Lilac, each with a solid powder-coated finish for a sleek, modern look.", "500ml Vacuum Bottle: Double-walled insulation keeps your drinks cold for longer, ensuring refreshing hydration all day long.", "Infuser Lid: The lid features a built-in infuser, perfect for adding flavour to your drinks with fruits, herbs, or tea.", "Premium 304 Stainless Steel: Durable inner and outer steel with a copper-plated lining for enhanced insulation and long-lasting durability.", "100% Leakproof & Puncture/Rust Resistant: Designed to be tough and reliable, making it the ideal bottle for everyday use.", "Customizable: Perfect for laser engraving or printing, ideal for personalizing or branding.", "Dishwasher Safe: Easy to clean (exclusive of decoration).", "Not Suitable for Hot or Carbonated Beverages or Food: Best used with cold drinks.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle comes individually packed in an eco-friendly BELL branded carton."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "23.5 x 7.5 cm diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Baby Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5002/bb5002-baby-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5002/bb5002-black.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/bb5002/bb5002-cream.webp"}, {"name": "Lilac", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w