  ('IntexGlobal','BB5005','Bell 3-In-1 Copper Vacuum Bottle Kit 950ml','bell-3-in-1-copper-vacuum-bottle-kit-950ml-bb5005','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','<p data-start="86" data-end="430">The <strong>Bell 3-In-1 Copper Vacuum Bottle</strong> Kit is your ultimate hydration companion, engineered for versatility, durability, and eco-conscious living. Crafted from recycled stainless steel and designed with a triple-lid system, this 950ml insulated bottle adapts effortlessly to every drinking style while delivering long-lasting temperature control.</p>
