  ('IntexGlobal','BMTD01','Rubber Bar Mat Bar Accessory','rubber-bar-mat-bar-accessory-bmtd01','Barware','Bar Accessories','The Rubber Bar Mat is a high-quality, custom-made bar accessory designed for functionality and brand visibility. Ideal for bars, restaurants, breweries, and promotional events, this durable mat protects countertops, absorbs spills, and enhances your brand presence.',1,true,false,'["Durable Rubber Material: Long-lasting, easy to clean, and resistant to spills.", "Custom Made to Order: Tailored to your size and logo requirements.", "Standard Pricing Based on 60cm x 25cm Size: Custom sizing options available.", "Non-Slip Surface: Ensures stability for glasses and bottles.", "Ideal for High-Traffic Areas: Perfect for bars, pubs, and hospitality venues.", "Branding Options Available: Can be printed or embossed with logos for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "60 (w) x 25 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/rubber-bar-mat/');
