  ('IntexGlobal','COLB16','Monaro Cooler Bag','monaro-cooler-bag-colb16','Bags','Cooler Bags','The Monaro Cooler Bag is a premium 6-can cooler bag designed for convenience, making it an excellent promotional item for outdoor events, corporate gifting, and everyday use. Its durable design, multiple compartments, and insulation ensure drinks and snacks stay fresh while on the go.',250,true,false,'["Durable 600D Nylon Material: Strong and long-lasting for repeated use.", "Holds Up to 6 Cans: Compact yet spacious enough for beverages and snacks.", "Top Compartment: Separate storage area for extra items, keeping them organized.", "Side Mesh Bottle Pocket: Provides easy access to water bottles or small accessories.", "Adjustable Webbed Carry Strap: Ensures comfortable and convenient carrying.", "Secure Zip Closure: Helps maintain insulation and temperature control.", "Available in Multiple Colours: Customizable to match your brand’s style.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for printing logos, event names, or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "24 (w) x 27 (h) x 15 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/colb16/colb16-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/colb16/colb16-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/colb16/colb16-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,6.2,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/monaro-cooler-bag/');
