  ('IntexGlobal','COSD05','Stainless Steel Coaster Bar Accessory','stainless-steel-coaster-bar-accessory-cosd05','Barware','Bar Accessories','The Stainless Steel Coaster Set is a modern and stylish addition to any home, office, or corporate setting. Designed for durability and surface protection, this set of four stainless steel coasters with rubber backing ensures a premium experience while enhancing your brand presence.',250,true,false,'["Set of 4 Stainless Steel Coasters: Sleek and modern, perfect for everyday use or special occasions.", "Rubber Backing: Prevents slipping and protects surfaces from scratches and moisture.", "Durable & Easy to Clean: Made from high-quality stainless steel for long-lasting use.", "Elegant Metallic Finish: Complements any table or workspace with a contemporary look.", "Heat & Stain Resistant: Ideal for both hot and cold beverages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "approx - 10 (D) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/cosd05/cosd05-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,4.62,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/stainless-steel-coaster/');
