  ('IntexGlobal','FRBN03','Foldable Nylon Fun Flyer Game & Puzzle','foldable-nylon-fun-flyer-game-puzzle-frbn03','Toys & Games','Games & Puzzles','The Foldable Nylon Fun Flyer is a fun and engaging promotional item, designed to attract attention at events, trade shows, and outdoor activities. Made from durable nylon, this flyer easily folds into a compact pouch for convenient storage and transport, making it a great giveaway for all ages.',250,true,false,'["Durable Nylon Material: Lightweight yet strong for long-lasting use.", "Foldable & Compact Design: Easily folds into an included pouch for portability.", "Fun & Interactive: Great for outdoor events, team-building activities, and brand exposure.", "Easy to Throw & Catch: Suitable for all skill levels, making it ideal for kids and adults.", "Perfect for Promotional Events: A unique and engaging way to showcase your brand."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.57,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/foldable-nylon-fun-flyer/');
