  ('IntexGlobal','JUTB04','Large Jute Shopping Bag','large-jute-shopping-bag-jutb04','Bags','Jute Bags','The Large Jute Shopping Bag is a strong, sustainable, and reusable shopping solution, perfect for retail, corporate giveaways, and eco-conscious promotions. Made from natural hessian jute, this bag is designed to carry heavier loads while promoting sustainability.',250,true,false,'["Premium Natural Hessian Jute: Durable, biodegradable, and environmentally friendly.", "Spacious Design: Provides ample storage for groceries, shopping, or everyday essentials.", "Reinforced Handles: Strong and comfortable for carrying heavier items with ease.", "Durable Construction: Built to withstand regular use and carry extra weight securely."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "30 (w) x 34 (h) x 18 (g)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/jutb04/jutb04-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.52,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/large-jute-shopping-bag/');
