  ('IntexGlobal','JUTB10','6 Can Jute Cooler Bag','6-can-jute-cooler-bag-jutb10','Bags','Jute Bags','The 6 Can Jute Cooler Bag is a sustainable and stylish insulated cooler bag, perfect for corporate giveaways, outdoor events, picnics, and eco-conscious promotions. Made from natural hessian jute, this bag features a durable insulated lining to keep drinks cool and wider natural cotton handles for comfortable carrying.',250,true,false,'["Premium Natural Hessian Jute: Strong, biodegradable, and environmentally friendly.", "Insulated Lining: Keeps beverages and food items cool and fresh.", "Holds Up to 6 Cans: Perfect for drinks, snacks, and small picnic essentials.", "Wider Natural Cotton Handles: Reinforced for added comfort and durability.", "Durable & Reusable: Designed for regular use while promoting sustainability."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "21(w) x 20(h) x 17(g)cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/jutb10/jutb10-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,3.89,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/6-can-jute-cooler-bag/');
