  ('IntexGlobal','MUGD05','Coffee Mug','coffee-mug-mugd05','Drinkware','Mugs','The 350ml Ceramic Coffee Mug is a timeless and practical choice for home, office, and promotional use. Designed for daily coffee or tea enjoyment, this mug offers a sleek and sturdy build, making it an ideal corporate gift, event giveaway, or retail item.',250,true,false,'["350ml Capacity: Perfect for coffee, tea, or hot beverages.", "Comfortable Handle: Ensures a secure and easy grip.", "Classic & Versatile Design: Suitable for office desks, cafés, and home kitchens.", "Handwash Recommended: Not dishwasher safe to maintain longevity.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "11 (h) x 9 (Dia) cm"}, {"name": "Durable Ceramic Construction", "value": "Designed for long-lasting use."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd05/mugd05-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd05/mugd05-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd05/mugd05-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd05/mugd05-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.42,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/coffee-mug/');
