  ('IntexGlobal','MUGD7125','325ml Coloured Stoneware Mug With C-Handle','325ml-coloured-stoneware-mug-with-c-handle-mugd7125','Drinkware','Mugs','The 325ml Coloured Stoneware Mug is a classic and functional choice for home, office, and promotional branding. Designed with a comfortable C-handle and available in a range of vibrant colours, this mug is perfect for coffee, tea, and hot beverages while showcasing your brand.',250,true,false,'["325ml Capacity: Ideal for coffee, tea, and other hot drinks.", "Durable Stoneware Construction: Built for everyday use.", "C-Handle Design: Ensures a comfortable and secure grip.", "Vibrant Colour Options: Matches various branding and personal styles.", "Handwash Recommended: Not dishwasher safe to maintain print and finish longevity.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8cm dia x 9 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Almond", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-almond.webp"}, {"name": "Black & White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-black-white.webp"}, {"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-black.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Lime Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-lime-green.webp"}, {"name": "Limegreen White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/mugd7125/mugd7125-limegreen-white.webp"}, {"name": "Navy & White", "hex": "", "i