  ('IntexGlobal','OC24X141','Frostbite Cooler Bag','frostbite-cooler-bag-oc24x141','Bags','Cooler Bags','The Frostbite Cooler Bag is a premium 6-can cooler bag designed for convenience, making it an excellent promotional item for outdoor events, corporate gifting, and everyday use. Its durable design, multiple compartments, and insulation ensure drinks and snacks stay fresh while on the go.',250,true,false,'["Durable 600D Nylon Material: Strong and long-lasting for repeated use.", "Holds Up to 6 Cans: Compact yet spacious enough for beverages and snacks.", "Side Mesh Bottle Pocket: Provides easy access to water bottles or small accessories.", "Adjustable Webbed Carry Strap: Ensures comfortable and convenient carrying.", "Secure Zip Closure: Helps maintain insulation and temperature control.", "Available in Multiple Colours: Customizable to match your brand’s style.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for printing logos, event names, or promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "22 (w) x 20 (h) x 16 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x141/oc24x141-black.webp"}, {"name": "Forest Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x141/oc24x141-forest-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x141/oc24x141-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Lime Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x141/oc24x141-lime-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x141/oc24x141-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_v