  ('IntexGlobal','OC24X148','Frostbite Jumbo 30-Can Cooler Cooler Bag','frostbite-jumbo-30-can-cooler-cooler-bag-oc24x148','Bags','Cooler Bags','The Frostbite Jumbo 30-Can Cooler is a heavy-duty, high-capacity cooler bag designed for outdoor adventures, corporate giveaways, and promotional branding. With its foil-lined insulation, multiple storage pockets, and comfortable carrying options, it’s the perfect companion for keeping food and drinks fresh on the go.',250,true,false,'["Heavy-Duty Construction: Built to withstand frequent use, making it ideal for outdoor events and travel.", "Holds Up to 30 Cans: Spacious interior for drinks, snacks, and meal storage.", "Foil Lining: Provides superior insulation to keep contents cooler for longer.", "Adjustable Webbed Straps: Ensures secure and comfortable carrying.", "Padded Shoulder Strap: Added comfort for extended carrying.", "Large Front Pocket: Extra storage for napkins, utensils, or other essentials.", "Side Mesh Pockets: Convenient for holding water bottles or additional items.", "Secure Zip Closure: Keeps items safely stored and maintains insulation.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for screen printing or embroidery of logos, making it an excellent promotional item."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "30 (w) x 20.5 (d) x 34 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x148/oc24x148-black.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x148/oc24x148-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc24x148/oc24x148-navy.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,10.4,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/frostbite-jumbo-30-can-cooler/');
