  ('IntexGlobal','OC30X168','AMG Folding Car Sunshade Car Accessory','amg-folding-car-sunshade-car-accessory-oc30x168','Tools & Auto','Car Accessories','The AMG Folding Car Sunshade is a durable and effective accessory designed to protect car interiors from heat and harmful UV rays. Made with reflective, silver-coated fabric, this sunshade helps keep the car cooler while preventing dashboard and seat damage. Featuring a foldable design with suction cups, it is easy to install, remove, and store, making it an ideal automotive giveaway or promotiona',250,true,false,'["Reflective Silver-Coated Fabric: Blocks heat and UV rays, keeping the car interior cooler.", "Foldable & Compact Design: Easily folds for convenient storage when not in use.", "Suction Cups Included: Ensures secure attachment to the windshield.", "Universal Fit: Suitable for most car windshields.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be printed with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "130 x 60 cm"}, {"name": "Lightweight & Easy to Use", "value": "Hassle-free setup and removal."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc30x168/oc30x168-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.85,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/folding-car-sunshade/');
