  ('IntexGlobal','OC35X230','Big Drawstring Shoe Pouch Drawstring Bag','big-drawstring-shoe-pouch-drawstring-bag-oc35x230','Bags','Drawstring Bags','The Big Drawstring Shoe Pouch is a spacious and functional promotional item designed to keep shoes protected while on the go. Perfect for travel, gyms, sports teams, and corporate giveaways, this pouch offers a convenient and stylish way to store footwear.',250,true,false,'["Spacious Design: Large enough to fit most shoe sizes, making it ideal for travel or sports use.", "Double Cord Drawstring Closure: Provides secure storage while allowing easy access.", "Durable Material: Designed to keep shoes protected from dust, dirt, and damage.", "Lightweight & Portable: Folds easily for compact storage when not in use.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: A sustainable alternative to disposable plastic shoe bags.", "Large Branding Area: Ideal for printing logos, slogans, or promotional messages for maximum brand exposure."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37 x 16 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc35x230/oc35x230-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.71,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/big-drawstring-shoe-pouch/');
