  ('IntexGlobal','OC514','Bamboo Tote Tote Bag','bamboo-tote-tote-bag-oc514','Bags','Tote Bags','The Bamboo Tote is a premium biodegradable and sustainable promotional bag, perfect for businesses looking to align their brand with eco-conscious values.',250,true,false,'["Sustainable Bamboo Material: Made from a renewable resource, offering a natural and biodegradable alternative to synthetic bags.", "Durable & Lightweight: Strong enough for everyday use while remaining lightweight and easy to carry.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: Promotes sustainability by reducing the need for plastic bags.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for printing logos, slogans, or promotional messages for maximum visibility.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for retail stores, corporate giveaways, trade shows, and environmentally focused promotions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37 (w) x 42 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc514/oc514-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.01,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bamboo-tote/');
