  ('IntexGlobal','OC9390','600ml Jupiter Glass Bottle With Neoprene Sleeve','600ml-jupiter-glass-bottle-with-neoprene-sleeve-oc9390','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 600ml Jupiter Glass Bottle is a sleek and eco-friendly drinkware solution, designed for daily hydration with a touch of style. Made from high-quality borosilicate glass, it features a secure screw-on stainless steel lid and a protective neoprene sleeve for insulation and added durability.',1,true,false,'["600ml Capacity: Ideal for staying hydrated throughout the day.", "Borosilicate Glass Construction: Lightweight, durable, and resistant to temperature changes.", "Neoprene Sleeve: Provides insulation, grip, and protection from minor impacts.", "Secure Screw-On Stainless Steel Lid: Ensures a leak-proof seal for on-the-go convenience.", "Modern & Stylish Design: Perfect for work, gym, outdoor activities, and travel.", "Reusable & Sustainable: A great alternative to plastic bottles."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.5 (d) x 23.8 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc9390/oc9390-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc9390/oc9390-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc9390/oc9390-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc9390/oc9390-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc9390/oc9390-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/600ml-jupiter-glass-bottle-with-neoprene-sleeve/');
