  ('IntexGlobal','OCA810395','Sunbus Sunglasses','sunbus-sunglasses-oca810395','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sunglasses','Elevate your look with <strong>Sunbus Sunglasses—</strong>the perfect blend of sleek urban style and natural elements. Featuring a durable plastic front paired with eco-friendly bamboo temples, these sunglasses combine comfort with conscious design. The metallic-finish lenses not only add a bold aesthetic but also provide reliable UV 400 protection, making them ideal for sunny days, festivals, or ',250,true,false,'["Plastic front frame with stylish bamboo temples.", "Reflective metallic lenses for a modern look.", "UV 400 protection shields eyes from harmful rays.", "Lightweight and comfortable for daily wear.", "Perfect for outdoor events, travel, and lifestyle promos."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "15 (w) x 5 (h) x 14 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Default", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.73,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/sunbus-sunglasses/');
