  ('IntexGlobal','OCBMS423','50% Recycled Natural Kraft Shopping Bag','50-recycled-natural-kraft-shopping-bag-ocbms423','Bags','Paper Bags','The 50% Recycled Natural Kraft Shopping Bag is a sturdy and sustainable packaging solution, ideal for retail, wine gifting, corporate events, and promotional giveaways. Made from 128gsm brown kraft paper, this bag is strong, practical, and environmentally conscious, featuring twisted paper handles for easy carrying.',250,true,false,'["50% Recycled Kraft Paper (128gsm): Durable, lightweight, and eco-friendly.", "Fits One Standard Wine Bottle: Ideal for gifting, retail, or special events.", "Twisted Paper Handles: Reinforced for comfortable and secure carrying.", "Natural Brown Kraft Finish: A classic and earthy look that complements sustainable branding.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for custom branding with logos and promotional messages."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "13(W) x 33(H) x 8(D)  cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbms423/ocbms423-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.26,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/50-recycled-natural-kraft-shopping-bag/');
