  ('IntexGlobal','OCBOPEN11','Credit Card Polished Bottle Opener','credit-card-polished-bottle-opener-ocbopen11','Barware','Bottle Openers','The Credit Card Polished Bottle Opener is a stylish and portable tool, designed for effortless bottle opening on the go. With its polished stainless steel finish and credit card-sized design, this opener fits easily into wallets, pockets, or cardholders, making it ideal for bars, events, corporate gifting, and promotional giveaways.',250,true,false,'["Premium Polished Stainless Steel: Durable, rust-resistant, and built for long-lasting use.", "Slim Credit Card Design: Easily fits into wallets or pockets for ultimate convenience.", "Effortless Bottle Opening: Designed for quick and smooth cap removal.", "Sleek & Stylish Finish: Adds a touch of sophistication to any barware collection.", "Lightweight & Portable: Perfect for everyday use, travel, or on-the-go convenience.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be personalized with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "5 (w) x 8 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen11/ocbopen11-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.76,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/credit-card-polished-bottle-opener/');
