  ('IntexGlobal','OCBOPEN8C','Paddle Style Powder Coated Steel Bottle Opener','paddle-style-powder-coated-steel-bottle-opener-ocbopen8c','Barware','Bottle Openers','The Paddle Style Powder Coated Steel Bottle Opener is a bartender-approved tool, designed for quick and efficient bottle opening. With its sleek powder-coated finish and durable steel construction, this speed opener is perfect for bars, restaurants, breweries, and promotional giveaways.',250,true,false,'["High-Quality Powder Coated Steel: Provides durability and a sleek, professional finish.", "Paddle-Style Design: Ensures fast and effortless cap removal, ideal for busy bartenders.", "Ergonomic & Comfortable Grip: Allows for easy handling and efficiency.", "Compact & Portable: Fits easily in a pocket, apron, or behind the bar.", "Perfect for High-Volume Use: Designed for professionals who need a reliable tool.", "Custom Branding Available: Can be customized with logos or designs for promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "18 (w) x 4 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen8c/ocbopen8c-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen8c/ocbopen8c-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen8c/ocbopen8c-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen8c/ocbopen8c-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocbopen8c/ocbopen8c-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/oc