  ('IntexGlobal','OCC109','Tyre Gauge Car Accessory','tyre-gauge-car-accessory-occ109','Tools & Auto','Car Accessories','The Tyre Gauge is a reliable and easy-to-use tool designed for measuring tyre pressure accurately up to 50 PSI. Made from durable aluminium, this compact gauge is an essential accessory for drivers, helping to maintain optimal tyre pressure for safety, fuel efficiency, and tyre longevity.',250,true,false,'["Measures up to 50 PSI: Ensures accurate tyre pressure readings.", "Durable Aluminium Construction: Lightweight yet strong for long-term use.", "Compact & Portable: Fits easily in a glove compartment, tool kit, or keychain.", "Easy to Use: Simple design for quick and efficient tyre checks.", "Ideal for Vehicle Safety & Maintenance: Helps improve fuel efficiency and tyre lifespan."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "15cm long"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ109/occ109-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ109/occ109-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ109/occ109-red.webp"}, {"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/occ109/occ109-silver.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.87,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/tyre-gauge/');
