  ('IntexGlobal','OCDR10','Flex Water Bottle With Carabiner','flex-water-bottle-with-carabiner-ocdr10','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The Flex Water Bottle with Carabiner is a convenient and space-saving hydration solution, perfect for travel, outdoor adventures, sports, and promotional giveaways. With its 473ml capacity, this foldable and reusable water bottle is designed for on-the-go use and can be rolled, folded, or flattened when empty for easy storage.',250,true,false,'["473ml Capacity: Ideal for daily hydration needs.", "Flexible & Foldable Design: Rolls, flattens, or folds when empty for compact storage.", "Durable & Reusable: Made from lightweight yet sturdy materials.", "Pull-Open Top: Easy to drink from and refill.", "Freezer-Safe: Can be frozen to keep water cool for longer.", "Carabiner Clip: Easily attaches to bags, belts, or backpacks for hands-free carrying."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "6.5cm x 22cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green Swirl", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-green-swirl.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink Swirl", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ocdr10/ocdr10-pink-swirl.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95