  ('IntexGlobal','PAPB01GLXL','Extra Large Full Coloured Laminated Bag','extra-large-full-coloured-laminated-bag-papb01glxl','Bags','Paper Bags','The Extra Large Full Colour Laminated Bag is a luxurious and durable promotional bag, perfect for corporate gifting, retail, trade shows, and high-end events. Made from 210gsm laminated paper, it features a glossy finish for a sleek, high-end look and strong rope handles for added durability and comfort.',250,true,false,'["Premium 210gsm Laminated Paper: Thick, durable, and designed for a luxury feel.", "Glossy Full-Colour Finish: Creates a high-impact, vibrant look that enhances branding.", "Strong Rope Handles: Provides a sturdy grip for comfortable carrying.", "Extra Large Size: Ideal for larger retail items, corporate gifts, and event giveaways.", "Large Branding Area: Perfect for full-colour printing of logos, marketing messages, or custom artwork for maximum visibility."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "Extra large: 42 (w) x 45 (h) x 15 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/papb01glxl/papb01glxl-green.webp"}, {"name": "Lime Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/papb01glxl/papb01glxl-lime-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/papb01glxl/papb01glxl-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/papb01glxl/papb01glxl-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/papb01glxl/papb01glxl-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.75,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/extra-large-full-coloured-l