  ('IntexGlobal','PS1204','Wheat Straw Slimline Black Eco Pen','wheat-straw-slimline-black-eco-pen-ps1204','Pens','Eco Pens','Introducing the Wheat Straw Slimline Black Pen, the perfect blend of sustainability and sleek design. With its slim profile, this pen is not only easy to carry but also ideal for quick, on-the-go note-taking. The black trimming adds a professional touch, making it a great choice for any brand.',100,true,true,'["Eco-Friendly Wheat Straw Barrel: Made from sustainable wheat straw, this pen is an environmentally conscious choice.", "Slim and Portable Design: Its slim profile allows for easy attachment to your body, making it convenient for instant use whenever needed.", "Push/Click Action: Provides smooth and reliable writing with a simple push of the button.", "Black Trimming: Elegant black accents that enhance its sleek and modern look.", "Customizable: Perfect for promotional purposes, with space to add your logo or branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "14cm X 1cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1204/ps1204-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1204/ps1204-green.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1204/ps1204-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1204/ps1204-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/wheat-straw-slimline-black/');
