  ('IntexGlobal','PS1602','Clear Pen Box Pen Presentation','clear-pen-box-pen-presentation-ps1602','Pens','Pen Presentation','Introducing the Clear Pen Box, a sleek and transparent case designed to complement your promotional pen. This simple yet elegant box ensures your pen is presented in the best possible light, making it a standout and memorable gift.',100,true,false,'["Transparent Design: The clear box allows your promotional pen to take center stage, showcasing its design and quality.", "Elegant and Professional: Simple, clean, and modern, making it an ideal packaging solution for corporate giveaways or branded gifts.", "Perfect Pairing: Matches seamlessly with any promotional pen, elevating the overall presentation and making it a thoughtful gift.", "Pen Sold Separately: This box is sold empty, allowing you to pair it with your choice of promotional pens."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "16cm x 3cm x 2cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Clear", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps1602/ps1602-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/clear-pen-box/');
