  ('IntexGlobal','PS2003','Central Coast Water Bottle - 800Ml','central-coast-water-bottle-800ml-ps2003','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Introducing the Central Coast Water Bottle, a sleek and practical 800ml stainless steel bottle designed for everyday use. Featuring a flip-top lid for easy access, this BPA-free bottle combines functionality with style.',50,true,false,'["800ml BPA-Free Stainless Steel: Safe, durable, and perfect for everyday hydration.", "Flip-Top Lid: Convenient for quick sips on the go, providing easy access to your drink.", "Available in 5 Colours: Choose from a range of vibrant colours to match your style or branding needs.", "Customizable: Perfect for rotary printing or engraving, offering a white finish for logos or designs.", "Not Suitable for Carbonated or Frozen Liquids: Best for still beverages.", "Not Recommended for Dishwasher Use: Hand wash to maintain the bottle’s appearance and performance.", "Eco-Friendly Gift Box: Packed individually in a sustainable gift box, making it a great option for gifts or promotional giveaways."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.2cm(dia) x 27.5cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2003/ps2003-black.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2003/ps2003-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2003/ps2003-royal.webp"}, {"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2003/ps2003-silver.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2003/ps2003-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex',