  ('IntexGlobal','PS2010','Bondi Vacuum Bottle With Bamboo Accent','bondi-vacuum-bottle-with-bamboo-accent-ps2010','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','<p data-start="78" data-end="520">Experience the perfect fusion of nature-inspired design and everyday practicality with the Bondi Vacuum Bottle with Bamboo Accent. Crafted from recycled stainless steel and finished with a sleek bamboo wrap, this 500ml insulated bottle is designed to keep your beverages at the ideal temperature while making a strong eco-conscious statement. Ideal for work, travel,',50,true,false,'["Double-walled recycled stainless steel construction with natural bamboo accent.", "Made using recycled metal for long-lasting durability and reduced environmental impact.", "Superior insulation keeps drinks hot or cold for hours.", "Shatter- and stain-resistant body for everyday use.", "Clean-taste interior engineered to ensure pure flavour with no metallic aftertaste.", "Suitable for rotary printing or laser engraving, revealing a premium shiny mirror finish.", "Eco-friendly design combining recycled materials with a natural bamboo wrap.", "Individually packed in a clean white box, ideal for gifting or corporate use.", "Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids; hand wash recommended to preserve bamboo finish."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.3cm (dia) x 21cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2010/ps2010-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2010/ps2010-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-vacuum-bottle-with-bamboo-accent/');
