  ('IntexGlobal','PS2013','Penski Vacuum Bottle','penski-vacuum-bottle-ps2013','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','<p data-start="72" data-end="388">Introducing the Penski Vacuum Bottle, thoughtfully designed to keep your drinks at the perfect temperature while adding a refined, eco-conscious touch to your daily routine. Crafted using recycled stainless steel and finished with elegant details, this bottle is ideal for everyday use, gifting, or premium branding.</p>',50,true,false,'["500ml double-walled vacuum bottle made from recycled stainless steel, BPA-free.", "Keeps drinks cold for up to 24 hours and hot for up to 12 hours.", "Premium matte finish delivers a sleek, modern, high-end look.", "Bamboo screw-top lid provides a secure, leak-proof, and eco-friendly seal.", "Shatter- and stain-resistant construction for long-lasting daily use.", "Suitable for rotary printing or engraving, revealing a shiny mirror finish for custom branding.", "Made with recycled metal to support sustainability and reduced environmental impact.", "Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids.", "Hand wash recommended to maintain finish and performance.", "Individually packed in an eco-friendly gift box, ideal for gifting or promotional use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7cm(dia) x 26.5cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2013/ps2013-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2013/ps2013-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/penski-vacuum-bottle/');
