  ('IntexGlobal','PS2018','Brit Bottle - 750Ml Single Wall','brit-bottle-750ml-single-wall-ps2018','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Promote your brand with the Brit Bottle 750ml, a sleek and versatile stainless steel bottle designed to leave a lasting impression. Ideal for events, giveaways, or corporate branding, it combines practicality with modern elegance.',50,true,false,'["Premium Soft-Feel Rubber Finish: A smooth, comfortable texture available in a variety of eye-catching colours.", "Generous 750ml Capacity: Perfect for staying hydrated throughout the day, whether at work, the gym, or on the go.", "Durable Stainless Steel Design: Crafted from BPA-free, single-walled stainless steel for safe and reliable use.", "Customizable for Your Brand: Ideal for rotary printing or engraving, ensuring your logo stands out with a polished finish.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each bottle is individually packed in a sustainable gift box, perfect for thoughtful gifting.", "Care Instructions: Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids. Hand washing recommended to maintain its premium finish."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.3cm Diameter x 22.5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Baby Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2018/ps2018-baby-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Blacku", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2018/ps2018-blacku.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2018/ps2018-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Cream", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2018/ps2018-cream.webp"}, {"name": "Crimson", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2018/ps2018-crimson.webp"}, {"name": "Mint