  ('IntexGlobal','PS2020','Brit Single Walled Bottle - 1L','brit-single-walled-bottle-1l-ps2020','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Make a bold statement with the Brit Single Walled Bottle 1L, a stylish and durable hydration solution perfect for your busy lifestyle. Designed with a premium soft-feel rubber finish and a generous capacity, this bottle ensures you stay hydrated in style.',50,true,false,'["Premium Soft-Feel Rubber Finish: Luxurious texture available in a range of chic colours for a sophisticated look.", "1L Single-Walled Stainless Steel Design: Lightweight yet durable, offering BPA-free safety for daily use.", "Shatter and Stain Resistant: Built to handle the rigors of your active routine without compromising on style.", "Customizable for Branding: Perfect for rotary printing or laser engraving, creating a glossy, professional finish.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it an ideal choice for gifts or promotions.", "Care Instructions: Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids. Hand washing recommended to maintain the soft-feel finish and durability."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.8cm Diameter x 25.5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2020/ps2020-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2020/ps2020-navy.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/brit-single-walled-bottle-1l/');
