  ('IntexGlobal','PS2021','Brit Vacuum Bottle - 1L','brit-vacuum-bottle-1l-ps2021','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Stay hydrated in style with the Brit Vacuum Bottle 1L, a premium insulated bottle designed for those who demand both performance and elegance. With a sleek soft-feel rubber finish and superior insulation, this bottle is perfect for all-day hydration at work, the gym, or on adventures.',50,true,false,'["Premium Soft-Feel Rubber Finish: Offers a luxurious grip and is available in a variety of sophisticated colours.", "1L Double-Walled Stainless Steel Design: Durable and BPA-free, ensuring safe and long-lasting use.", "Superior Insulation: Keeps beverages cold for up to 24 hours or hot for up to 12 hours, perfect for any season.", "Shatter and Stain Resistant: Built to handle everyday use without losing its sleek appearance.", "Customizable for Branding: Ideal for rotary printing or engraving, providing a shiny mirror finish for a professional touch.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, making it perfect for gifting or promotional use.", "Care Instructions: Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids. Hand washing recommended to maintain the premium soft-feel finish and insulation performance."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8.4cm Diameter x 28.5 H cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2021/ps2021-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2021/ps2021-navy.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/brit-vacuum-bottle-1l/');
