  ('IntexGlobal','PS2028','1L Stainless Steel Thermos with Silicone Handle Drink Bottle','1l-stainless-steel-thermos-with-silicone-handle-drink-bottle-ps2028','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 1L Stainless Steel Thermos with Silicone Handle is the perfect blend of durability, functionality, and style—crafted to handle everything from daily commutes to outdoor adventures. Its generous 1-liter capacity keeps you hydrated longer, while the rugged stainless steel body ensures lasting performance and resistance to wear. The addition of a premium ceramic-coated interior provides a cleaner',25,true,false,'["1L (1000ml) capacity reduces frequent refills.", "High-quality stainless steel construction for long-lasting durability.", "Ceramic-coated interior prevents metallic taste and maintains beverage purity.", "Silicone handle for comfortable, secure carrying and easy attachment to bags or gear.", "Suitable for both hot and cold drinks with excellent temperature retention.", "Leak-proof lid design prevents spills during transport.", "Sleek stainless steel finish for a modern, professional look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "22.5(h) x 9.5(Dia) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2028/ps2028-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/1l-stainless-steel-thermos-with-silicone-handle/');
