  ('IntexGlobal','PS2223M','Moama Glass Coffee Cup - 350Ml With Silicon Lid And Band','moama-glass-coffee-cup-350ml-with-silicon-lid-and-band-ps2223m','Drinkware','Coffee Cups','The Moama Glass Coffee Cup is the perfect blend of sustainability, style, and functionality, ideal for enjoying your coffee on the go.',50,true,false,'["Premium Borosilicate Glass: Made from single-walled borosilicate glass for durability and clarity.", "Silicone Lid and Band: Offers a secure, spill-resistant lid and a comfortable grip, available in a wide range of colours to suit your style or branding.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Each cup is packed in an eco-friendly gift box, making it perfect for gifting or promotions.", "Generous 350ml Capacity: Perfect for coffee, tea, or any hot beverages.", "Handwash Recommended: To maximise the lifespan of your logo or design."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "7.5cm (D) x 12.5cm (H)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-black.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2223m/ps2223m-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/