  ('IntexGlobal','PS2301','Fitness Shaker - 600Ml Drink Bottle','fitness-shaker-600ml-drink-bottle-ps2301','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Stay hydrated and fuel your workouts with the 600ml Fitness Shaker. Designed for smooth mixing, it features a secure screw-on lid, snap closure, and a stainless steel mixing ball to ensure lump-free shakes every time. Perfect for protein shakes, supplements, or daily hydration on the go.',50,true,false,'["Large 600ml Capacity – Ideal for protein shakes and supplements", "Secure Screw-On Lid – Leak-resistant and reliable", "Snap Closure – Easy to open and close while on the move", "Stainless Steel Mixing Ball – Ensures smooth, well-mixed drinks", "Durable & Lightweight – Great for the gym, office, or travel"]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "22cm x 9.5cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2301/ps2301-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2301/ps2301-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps2301/ps2301-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/fitness-shaker-600ml/');
