  ('IntexGlobal','PS4003','Kansas Tote Bag','kansas-tote-bag-ps4003','Bags','Tote Bags','Make a lasting impression with the versatile and customizable Kansas Tote Bag. Perfect for grocery shopping, retail use, or daily job, it’s the ideal promotional item for showcasing your brand in style.',100,true,false,'["Durable and Lightweight: Made from 80gsm non-woven polypropylene material, combining strength with portability.", "Spacious Design: Dimensions of 36cm W x 41cm H x 11.5cm provide ample room for groceries, shopping, or essentials.", "Convenient Carrying: Extended handles ensure comfortable over-the-shoulder use for effortless mobility.", "Customizable Branding Area: Add a personalized 25cm x 25cm design for maximum visibility and impact.", "Vibrant Color Options: Available in Black, Yellow, Pink, Purple, Green, Maroon, Red, White, Orange, Navy, Royal, Bottle Green, and Grey to match your brand aesthetic."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36cm W x 41cm H x 11.5cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-black.webp"}, {"name": "Bottle Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-bottle-green.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Light Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4003/ps4003-light-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Mar