  ('IntexGlobal','PS4003L','Kansas Laminated Tote Bag','kansas-laminated-tote-bag-ps4003l','Bags','Tote Bags','The Kansas Laminated Tote Bag is your go-to solution for vibrant, full-color branding. Its spacious design and premium finish make it perfect for promotional events, retail use, and everyday errands.',1,true,false,'["Premium Laminated Finish: A sleek, glossy surface adds a polished look while ensuring durability and easy cleaning.", "Spacious Design: Measuring 36cm x 41cm, it offers ample room for groceries, shopping, or essentials.", "Full-Color Customization: Personalize the entire bag, from base to handles, with vivid, full-color designs for maximum branding impact.", "Large Print Area: Showcase your unique 36cm x 41cm image to make a lasting impression.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for promotions, events, and daily use, blending functionality with standout style."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36cm x 41cm x 11cm gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kansas-laminated-tote-bag/');
