  ('IntexGlobal','PS4004','Detroit Tote Bag','detroit-tote-bag-ps4004','Bags','Tote Bags','The Detroit Tote Bag combines durability and functionality, making it the perfect companion for grocery shopping and daily errands. Its spacious design and customizable options ensure it stands out as a reliable and stylish promotional item.',100,true,false,'["Durable Material: Crafted from 80gsm non-woven polypropylene, ensuring strength and longevity.", "Spacious Interior: Measuring 31cm x 34cm x 20cm, it offers ample room for bulky grocery items and more.", "Secure Double Handles: Designed for a comfortable grip and reliable support to keep your goods safe.", "Customizable Branding Area: Add a 10cm x 17cm image for a personalized touch and unique brand impression.", "Variety of Colors: Available in Black, Green, Grey, Navy, Orange, Pink, Purple, Red, Royal, White, and Yellow to match your style or branding needs."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31cm x 34cm x 20cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Bottle Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-bottle-green.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-green.webp"}, {"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Light Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4004/ps4004-light-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Maroon", "hex": "", "image