  ('IntexGlobal','PS4004L','Detroit Laminated Tote Bag','detroit-laminated-tote-bag-ps4004l','Bags','Tote Bags','The Detroit Laminated Tote Bag offers a sleek and vibrant solution for your promotional needs. With its full-color customization, this tote bag is perfect for making a bold and lasting impression.',1,true,false,'["Premium Laminated Finish: Durable, glossy surface for a polished and professional look.", "Spacious Design: Measuring 31cm x 34cm x 20cm, it provides ample space for essentials, groceries, or promotional materials.", "Full-Color Customization: Personalize the bag from base to handle with vibrant, eye-catching designs for maximum impact.", "Generous Branding Area: Showcase your unique 31cm x 34cm image for a distinctive and memorable impression.", "Versatile and Stylish: Ideal for events, retail, or daily use, combining practicality with high-impact branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31cm x 34cm x 20cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/detroit-laminated-tote-bag/');
