  ('IntexGlobal','PS4010L','Ohio Laminated Tote Bag','ohio-laminated-tote-bag-ps4010l','Bags','Tote Bags','The Ohio Laminated Tote Bag is the perfect promotional companion for retail, trade shows, and everyday use. With its tall design and customizable full-color print, it''s an eye-catching way to showcase your brand.',1,true,false,'["Durable Laminated Finish: A glossy, easy-to-clean surface that enhances durability and adds a sleek look.", "Tall and Spacious Design: With dimensions of 28cm x 32cm x 10cm, this tote offers ample space for essentials while maintaining a compact form.", "Full-Color Customization: Personalize the entire bag, from base to handles, with vibrant, full-color designs for maximum branding impact.", "Large Branding Area: Customize with your 28cm x 32cm image for a unique and memorable impression.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for retail, trade shows, or daily activities, combining functionality with bold branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "28cm x 32cm x 10cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/ohio-laminated-tote-bag/');
