  ('IntexGlobal','PS4011L','Hollywood Laminated Tote Bag','hollywood-laminated-tote-bag-ps4011l','Bags','Tote Bags','The Hollywood Laminated Tote Bag offers a sleek and durable design, perfect for showcasing your brand with full-color customization. Its spacious size and vibrant print options make it an ideal promotional tool for events, retail, and more.',1,true,false,'["Premium Laminated Finish: Durable, glossy surface adds style while making it easy to clean.", "Generous Size: Measuring 40cm x 32cm x 12cm, this bag provides ample space for groceries, shopping, or promotional materials.", "Full-Color Customization: Personalize the bag from base to handles with vibrant, eye-catching designs to leave a lasting impression.", "Large Branding Area: Customize with your 40cm x 32cm image for maximum visibility and impact.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for retail, trade shows, events, or everyday use, combining practicality with bold branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40cm x 32cm x 12cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/hollywood-laminated-tote-bag/');
