  ('IntexGlobal','PS4026','Noosa A4 Non Woven Promo Bag','noosa-a4-non-woven-promo-bag-ps4026','Bags','Tote Bags','The Noosa A4 Non-Woven Promo Bag is a compact and versatile tote that packs a punch in terms of promotional impact. Perfect for trade shows, conventions, and everyday marketing, this bag is the ideal choice for businesses looking to leave a lasting impression.',100,true,false,'["Compact Size: A convenient A4 size, ideal for carrying documents, promotional materials, or daily essentials.", "Durable Non-Woven Material: Made from sturdy, lightweight non-woven material for reliability and easy portability.", "Custom Branding Area: A 14cm x 14cm print area, making customization easy for your logo or design.", "Color Options: Available in Bottle Green, Black, Green, Grey, Navy, Orange, Pink, Red, Royal, White, and Yellow to match your brand or event theme.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for trade shows, conventions, retail, and everyday use, offering ample opportunity for branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "27cm W x 34.5cm H x 6cm L"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Grey", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4026/ps4026-grey.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4026/ps4026-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4026/ps4026-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4026/ps4026-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Purple", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4026/ps4026-purple.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/p