  ('IntexGlobal','PS4101','Indiana Short Handle Calico Bag','indiana-short-handle-calico-bag-ps4101','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Indiana Short Handle Calico Bag combines convenience, durability, and eco-friendliness, making it the perfect choice for a variety of uses. Whether you''re attending trade shows, conventions, retail events, or simply running errands, this bag offers a stylish and sustainable solution for carrying your essentials.',100,true,false,'["Durable 140-GSM Calico Fabric: Made from sturdy, eco-friendly calico material, offering a sustainable choice for everyday use.", "Convenient Size: Measures 38cm x 42cm, providing ample space for your essentials while remaining compact and portable.", "Practical Short Handle: The 40cm short handle ensures comfortable carrying, making it ideal for quick trips or events.", "Custom Branding Area: Personalize with a 25cm x 25cm print area, perfect for showcasing your logo or message.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for trade shows, conventions, retail, or daily activities, offering great potential for brand promotion."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 42cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4101/ps4101-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/indiana-short-handle-calico-bag/');
