  ('IntexGlobal','PS4105','Snapper Calico Sling Bag','snapper-calico-sling-bag-ps4105','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Snapper Calico Sling Bag is the perfect combination of convenience and style. Featuring a natural color and a long, adjustable sling handle, this bag is designed for easy, hands-free carrying.',100,true,false,'["Durable 140gsm Natural Calico Fabric: Made from eco-friendly, sturdy calico fabric, offering a sustainable and practical option for everyday use.", "Ample Space: Bag size 33cm(w) x 39cm(h) x 6cm gusset, providing plenty of room for personal items, merchandise, or event essentials.", "Long Sling Handle: The 5cm(w) x 13cm(h) shoulder strap ensures comfortable carrying for hands-free convenience, making it ideal for travel or daily errands.", "Custom Branding Area: The large 25cm x 25cm print area allows for easy customization to display your logo or promotional message.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for retail, trade shows, conferences, or even as a stylish everyday bag."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "Bag Size: 33(w) x 39(h) x 6(gusset) cm,   Shoulder Strap: 5(w) x 13(h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4105/ps4105-natural.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/snapper-calico-sling-bag/');
