  ('IntexGlobal','PS4107','Coloured Calico Bag Short Handle','coloured-calico-bag-short-handle-ps4107','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Coloured Calico Bag with Short Handle is the perfect combination of eco-friendliness and practicality. Made from 100% renewable and reusable cotton, this 130gsm bag is designed to make a positive impact on both your brand and the environment.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly and Renewable: Crafted from 100% cotton, this bag is both sustainable and reusable, making it a great choice for environmentally conscious brands.", "Durable 130gsm Calico Fabric: Strong and reliable, perfect for everyday use or carrying heavier items.", "Spacious Design: Measures 38cm W x 42cm H, offering ample space for your items, promotional materials, or groceries.", "Short Handle Design: The sturdy short handle makes it easy to carry, providing both comfort and convenience.", "Custom Branding Area: A large 25cm x 25cm print area allows for easy customization, ensuring your logo or message stands out.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for retail, trade shows, conventions, or as an everyday bag for groceries, books, and more."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm W x 42cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4107/ps4107-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4107/ps4107-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/coloured-calico-bag-short-handle/');
