  ('IntexGlobal','PS4111','Large Calico Bag White','large-calico-bag-white-ps4111','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The Large Calico Bag White is the perfect promotional accessory to showcase your brand with style and simplicity. Crafted from durable calico fabric, this bag features a clean white design and a convenient short handle, making it ideal for various occasions such as trade shows, retail, events, or everyday use.',100,true,false,'["Durable and Eco-Friendly: Made from high-quality 140gsm calico fabric, this bag is both sustainable and long-lasting.", "Generous Print Area: The large 25cm x 25cm customization space allows you to prominently display your logo, artwork, or promotional message.", "Simple and Clean Design: The white color provides a blank canvas that highlights your design, making it ideal for brand promotions.", "Convenient Short Handle: The sturdy short handle ensures comfort and easy carrying for everyday use.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for trade shows, retail, events, and even daily errands."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36.5cm W x 40.5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4111/ps4111-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/large-calico-bag-white/');
