  ('IntexGlobal','PS4112','White Calico Bag With Long Handles','white-calico-bag-with-long-handles-ps4112','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','The White Calico Bag with Long Handles is an ideal choice for promoting your brand while offering practicality and style. Its natural white color serves as a clean canvas to showcase your custom design, ensuring your logo or message stands out.',100,true,false,'["Durable and Eco-Friendly: Made from high-quality 140gsm calico fabric, this bag is both sturdy and sustainable, ideal for everyday use.", "Generous Customization Area: With a large 25cm x 25cm print area, you can prominently display your logo, artwork, or promotional message.", "Convenient Long Handles: The long handles make this bag easy to carry over the shoulder, providing comfort for extended use.", "Spacious Design: The 40cm x 36cm x 9.5cm size provides ample space for carrying a variety of items, from books to retail products.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for retail, trade shows, events, and even daily errands."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36cm W x 40cm H x 9.5cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4112/ps4112-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/white-calico-bag-with-long-handles/');
