  ('IntexGlobal','PS4202','Minnesota Canvas Natural Tote Bag','minnesota-canvas-natural-tote-bag-ps4202','Bags','Tote Bags','The Minnesota Canvas Natural Tote Bag is the perfect blend of sustainability, style, and functionality. With a large print area and a timeless natural color, it''s an ideal choice for retail, trade shows, and everyday use.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly and Durable: Made from 320gsm canvas, this tote is reusable and built to last, offering a sustainable choice for carrying essentials.", "Customizable Design: The generous 25cm x 25cm print area gives you plenty of space to showcase your logo, brand, or artwork, ensuring maximum visibility.", "Spacious and Practical: With a size of 38cm x 42cm, this bag offers ample space for carrying items to and from events, shops, or daily activities.", "Comfortable to Carry: The double long handles make it easy to carry even heavy loads comfortably.", "Perfect for Promotions: Ideal for retail, trade shows, and other promotional events, ensuring your message is seen everywhere the bag goes."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 42cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4202/ps4202-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/minnesota-canvas-natural-tote-bag/');
