  ('IntexGlobal','PS4203','Denver Canvas Coloured Tote Bag','denver-canvas-coloured-tote-bag-ps4203','Bags','Tote Bags','The Denver Canvas Tote Bag is the perfect combination of durability, spaciousness, and style. Crafted from strong 330gsm woven material, this tote is designed to withstand daily use while offering a large custom print area to showcase your brand.',100,true,false,'["Durable Material: Made from 330gsm woven canvas, this tote is strong, reliable, and built to last.", "Spacious Design: With dimensions of 41cm W x 37cm H x 7.5cm D, this tote offers ample room for your belongings, making it perfect for daily use or events.", "Customizable Print Area: Featuring a generous 25cm x 25cm print space, your logo or design can be easily showcased with high-quality screen printing.", "Multiple Color Handles: Available in Natural, Black, Blue, and Red.", "Versatile and Practical: Perfect for retail, trade shows, conferences, and more, this tote provides both functionality and a modern look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "41cm W x 37cm H x 7.5cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4203/ps4203-black.webp"}, {"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4203/ps4203-natural.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4203/ps4203-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4203/ps4203-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/denver-canvas-coloured-tote-bag/');
