  ('IntexGlobal','PS4204','Idaho Canvas Bag','idaho-canvas-bag-ps4204','Bags','Tote Bags','The Idaho Canvas Bag combines durability with practicality, making it the ideal companion for beach trips, retail shopping, and everyday use. Made from eco-friendly 340gsm (12oz) woven material, this bag is designed to withstand daily wear while offering ample storage space and organization with multiple pockets.',100,true,false,'["Durable and Eco-Friendly: Crafted from strong 340gsm (12oz) woven material, this bag is built to last while being environmentally conscious.", "Spacious Design: Measuring 40cm x 55cm x 15cm, the bag provides a wide open main compartment with plenty of room for your essentials.", "Efficient Storage: Equipped with inside and outside pockets, the Idaho bag helps keep your items organized and easily accessible.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for retail shopping, beach trips, or everyday activities, this bag combines function and style.", "Customizable Print Area: Features a 10cm x 10cm print area, making it easy to add your logo or design for a personalized touch.", "Available in Stylish Colors: Choose from black, blue, or red to match your preferences and branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40cm x 55cm x 15cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4204/ps4204-black.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4204/ps4204-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4204/ps4204-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/idaho-canvas-bag/');
