  ('IntexGlobal','PS4205','James Natural Canvas Tote Bag','james-natural-canvas-tote-bag-ps4205','Bags','Tote Bags','The James Natural Canvas Tote Bag is a perfect combination of durability and functionality. Made from 280gsm canvas, this bag is designed to withstand daily use while offering plenty of space for your essentials.',100,true,false,'["Durable Material: Crafted from 280gsm canvas for long-lasting durability, perfect for everyday use and events.", "Spacious Design: Measures 37cm W x 40cm H x 10cm base gusset, providing ample space for carrying your items.", "Reinforced Handles: Strong, durable long handles ensure comfort and reliability while carrying heavy or bulky items.", "Customizable: Features a large 25cm x 25cm print area, allowing for easy customization with your logo or design for a unique, promotional touch.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for trade shows, conventions, retail, and daily activities, this tote bag serves a variety of purposes.", "Eco-Friendly: Made from natural canvas, an environmentally friendly choice for those looking to reduce their carbon footprint."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37cm W x 40cm H x 10cm base gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205/ps4205-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/james-natural-canvas-tote-bag/');
