  ('IntexGlobal','PS4205C','James Coloured Canvas Tote Bag','james-coloured-canvas-tote-bag-ps4205c','Bags','Tote Bags','The James Coloured Canvas Tote Bag is a durable and versatile accessory that combines practicality with a customizable touch. Made from 280gsm canvas, this bag is built to last and is perfect for a variety of uses, from trade shows and conventions to daily shopping and errands.',100,true,false,'["Durable Construction: Made from 280gsm canvas, ensuring long-lasting use even under heavy loads.", "Spacious Design: Measures 37cm W x 40cm H x 10cm base gusset, offering ample room for carrying everyday items, groceries, and more.", "Reinforced Dual Handles: Strong, sturdy handles for easy carrying, designed for maximum durability and comfort.", "Customizable Print Area: Large 25cm W x 25cm H print area allows for easy customization with your logo, message, or artwork.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for trade shows, conventions, daily shopping, and retail use, making it perfect for both personal and promotional purposes.", "Custom Colours: Available in various colours, making it easy to match your brand''s aesthetic or create a unique look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37cm W x 40cm H x 10cm base gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-black.webp"}, {"name": "Camel", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-camel.webp"}, {"name": "Charcoal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-charcoal.webp"}, {"name": "Olive", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-olive.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-red.webp"}, {"name": "Sage Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-sage-green.webp"}, {"name": "Sage Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4205c/ps4205c-sage-navy.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/james-coloured-canvas-tote-bag/');
