  ('IntexGlobal','PS4206','Maxi Natural Canvas Tote Bag','maxi-natural-canvas-tote-bag-ps4206','Bags','Tote Bags','The Maxi Canvas Tote Bag is the perfect sustainable solution for everyday shopping, retail, and trade shows. Designed to replace plastic bags, it offers a large print area for easy customization, making it ideal for promotional purposes or personal use.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly & Durable: Made from 280gsm canvas, this reusable tote bag is a sustainable alternative to plastic bags, built to last for everyday use.", "Generous Size: Measures 32cm x 45cm x 12cm gusset, providing ample space for groceries, retail items, and other essentials.", "Customizable: The large 25cm x 25cm print area allows you to easily personalize the bag with your logo, artwork, or message for a unique and lasting impression.", "Convenient & Practical: Perfect for trade shows, conventions, retail, and daily shopping, offering a simple, sturdy, and eco-friendly solution for carrying goods."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "45cm W x 32cm H x 12cm gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4206/ps4206-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/maxi-natural-canvas-tote-bag/');
