  ('IntexGlobal','PS4207','Manly PolyCanvas Bag','manly-polycanvas-bag-ps4207','Bags','Tote Bags','The Manly PolyCanvas Bag is an eco-friendly and reusable tote bag designed to replace plastic bags while offering a durable and stylish option for everyday use. With its simple and functional design, this Polycanvas tote is perfect for retail, trade shows, and general shopping, ensuring you carry your essentials in an environmentally conscious way.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly & Reusable: Made from durable PolyCanvas material 65% polyester, 35% cotton, this bag is designed to reduce plastic waste, making it a sustainable choice for the environment.", "Generous Size: Measures 38cm x 42cm, providing ample space for shopping, groceries, or other daily essentials.", "Customizable: The 25cm x 25cm print area allows for easy customization with your logo, artwork, or message, leaving a lasting impression on customers or event attendees.", "Practical & Versatile: Perfect for retail, trade shows, conventions, and everyday use, offering a simple, stylish, and sustainable solution to your carrying needs.", "Clean Design: The classic natural color makes it ideal for showcasing custom designs and logos."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm x 42cm"}, {"name": "Material", "value": "280gsm."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4207/ps4207-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/manly-polycanvas-bag/');
