  ('IntexGlobal','PS4210','Bondi Canvas Tote Bag - Coloured','bondi-canvas-tote-bag-coloured-ps4210','Bags','Tote Bags','The Bondi Canvas Tote Bag in vibrant colours is the ultimate combination of style and functionality. Made from durable 100% canvas material.',100,true,false,'["Generous Dimensions: Measures 42cm (W) x 23cm (H) x 36cm (gusset) for plenty of room to store your essentials.", "High-Quality Material: Constructed from 280gsm 100% canvas for durability and strength.", "Multiple Pockets: Features both internal and external pockets, plus an internal zipper pocket to secure smaller items.", "Colour Options: Available in Black, Navy, Camel, and Petrol Blue, providing variety for every style and preference.", "Long Handles: The extended handles make it comfortable to carry over the shoulder or by hand.", "Customizable: Ideal for screen printing or full-colour transfers, offering a large print area for your logo, artwork, or promotional designs."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "42cm(w) x 36(h) x 23(gusset)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4210/ps4210-black.webp"}, {"name": "Camel", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4210/ps4210-camel.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4210/ps4210-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Petrol Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4210/ps4210-petrol-blue.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-canvas-tote-bag-coloured/');
