  ('IntexGlobal','PS4211','Brighton Duffle Bag','brighton-duffle-bag-ps4211','Bags','Tote Bags','Introducing the Brighton Duffle Bag, a perfect blend of style, sustainability, and practicality. The outer shell is crafted from soft, recycled denim, while the inner lining is made from 100% cotton, offering a durable and environmentally conscious solution for your carrying needs.',50,true,false,'["Spacious Design: Measures 50cm (L) x 23cm (W) x 35cm (H), providing ample room for clothes, accessories, and more.", "Eco-Friendly Materials: Made from 320gsm recycled denim for the outer fabric and 180gsm -100% cotton for the inner lining, promoting sustainability.", "Comfortable Carrying: Equipped with a long handle for easy hand carrying and an adjustable, removable shoulder strap for versatile carrying options.", "Customizable: Perfect for embroidery or full-color transfer, offering a large surface for your personal touch or brand logo.", "Durable & Stylish: The high-quality materials ensure lasting durability while maintaining a fashionable look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "50cm (L) x 23cm (W) x 35cm (H)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4211/ps4211-black.webp"}, {"name": "Denim Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4211/ps4211-denim-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4211/ps4211-navy-blue.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/brighton-duffle-bag/');
