  ('IntexGlobal','PS4402','Nylon Foldable Bag','nylon-foldable-bag-ps4402','Bags','Tote Bags','The Nylon Foldable Bag is designed for those who value practicality without compromising on style. Measuring 38cm (w) x 48cm (h), this shopping bag offers ample space for carrying groceries, clothes, or everyday essentials. What makes it even more special is its foldable feature—once you''ve finished using it, simply fold the bag into itself and secure it with a drawstring. This allows for easy sto',100,true,false,'["Foldable Design: Easily folds into itself and secures with a drawstring, perfect for compact storage.", "Spacious and Practical: With a generous 38cm (W) x 48cm (H) size, it’s ideal for shopping or carrying everyday items.", "Customizable: Personalize your bag with your design or logo using a 20cm x 20cm print area.", "Durable and Lightweight: Made from high-quality nylon for long-lasting use, while remaining lightweight and easy to carry.", "Colour Options: Available in black, navy, red, royal, and white, allowing you to choose the perfect match for your style or branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "38cm(w) x 48cm(h)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4402/ps4402-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4402/ps4402-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4402/ps4402-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4402/ps4402-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4402/ps4402-white.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https:/