  ('IntexGlobal','PS4506','Laminated Jute Supermarket Bag','laminated-jute-supermarket-bag-ps4506','Bags','Jute Bags','The Laminated Jute Supermarket Bag is the perfect solution for eco-conscious shoppers. Made from 100% hessian jute, this durable bag is designed to carry fresh produce while maintaining an environmentally friendly approach.',100,true,false,'["Spacious Design: Measures 40cm x 32cm x 18cm with a large gusset, offering plenty of room for fresh produce and other groceries.", "Eco-Friendly: Made from 100% hessian jute, this bag is both durable and sustainable, reducing your carbon footprint.", "Practical Storage: The large gusset allows the bag to be easily folded for compact storage when not in use.", "Customizable: Personalize with a laminated 25cm x 18cm design for a unique promotional touch.", "Colour: Available in a natural colour, adding a rustic, organic feel to your shopping experience."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40cm x 32cm x 18cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4506/ps4506-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/laminated-jute-supermarket-bag-2/');
