  ('IntexGlobal','PS4507','Laminated Jute Supermarket Bag With Coloured Handles And Gussets','laminated-jute-supermarket-bag-with-coloured-handles-and-gussets-ps4507','Bags','Jute Bags','This Laminated Jute Supermarket Bag combines durability, eco-friendliness, and style. Made from 100% hessian, this large, reusable bag is perfect for your supermarket trips, shopping, and more. The bag’s sturdy design features coloured handles and gussets, offering both functionality and a stylish touch.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 40cm x 32cm x 18cm, providing ample space for groceries, produce, or everyday essentials.", "Eco-Friendly: Made from 100% hessian jute, a natural and biodegradable material that’s both sustainable and durable.", "Customisable Design: Personalise your bag with a 25cm x 18cm design area, perfect for logos, branding, or unique artwork.", "Colour Variety: Choose from handles and gussets in black, green, navy, red, or royal to match your branding or personal style.", "Practical and Reliable: Ideal for heavy-duty shopping trips, this bag is built to last and can be reused time and again, reducing the need for plastic bags."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40cm x 32cm x 18cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4507/ps4507-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4507/ps4507-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4507/ps4507-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4507/ps4507-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4507/ps4507-royal-blue.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/laminated-jute-supermarket-bag-with-coloured-handles-and-gussets/');
