  ('IntexGlobal','PS4512','Juco Bag','juco-bag-ps4512','Bags','Jute Bags','Elevate your brand or carry your essentials in style with the Juco Bag. Crafted from a premium blend of jute and cotton, this bag offers a sustainable and durable solution for various uses.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 40 cm (W) x 32 cm (H) x 16 cm gusset, offering plenty of space for shopping, events, or daily essentials.", "Material: Made from high-quality juco, a blend of jute and cotton, providing strength and eco-friendliness.", "Comfortable Carrying: Equipped with soft, padded handles for easy and comfortable carrying, even when the bag is full.", "Customisation: Large print area perfect for full-color transfers, enabling you to prominently showcase your logo or design for maximum visibility.", "Eco-Friendly: A stylish, environmentally conscious choice, combining sustainability with a modern, versatile design.", "Versatile: Ideal for retail, shopping, events, conferences, and everyday use, making it a functional and fashionable choice."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40(w) x 32(h) x 16cm gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4512/ps4512-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/juco-bag/');
