  ('IntexGlobal','PS4514','Hemp Tote Bag with Gusset','hemp-tote-bag-with-gusset-ps4514','Bags','Cotton Tote Bags','Introducing the Hemp Tote Bag with Gusset—the ideal combination of style, sustainability, and practicality. Made from 100% organic hemp fibers, this tote bag provides durability and versatility for a range of uses, while making a positive contribution to the environment.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 37 cm (W) x 40 cm (H) x 10 cm base gusset — offering spacious capacity for your everyday essentials, groceries, or promotional items.", "Material: Crafted from 100% organic 140gsm hemp fibers, known for their strength and natural texture, providing a sustainable and eco-friendly alternative to synthetic fabrics.", "Eco-Friendly: A sustainable choice that supports environmental conservation by reducing reliance on non-renewable resources.", "Customisation: The large print area is perfect for branding, logos, or unique designs, ensuring a lasting and impactful promotional message.", "Enhanced Capacity: The base gusset adds extra space, making this bag ideal for shopping, retail, trade shows, or daily activities.", "Versatile Use: Whether for personal use or as a promotional product, this hemp tote is practical for any occasion."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "37cm W x 40cm H x 10cm base gusset"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4514/ps4514-natural.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/hemp-tote-bag-with-gusset/');
