  ('IntexGlobal','PS4601L','Kraft Paper Bag Brown Large Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-brown-large-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4601l','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag Brown Large with Twisted Paper Handle—a practical and eco-friendly choice for retail, events, and promotional needs. This sustainable paper bag combines durability with style, featuring strong twisted paper handles for easy and comfortable carrying.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 31 cm (W) x 42 cm (H) x 11 cm (G) — offering ample space for retail products, gifts, or promotional materials", "Material: Made from 130gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is a sustainable and biodegradable option, reducing the environmental impact of plastic bags", "Twisted Paper Handles: Durable and sturdy twisted paper handles provide a secure and comfortable grip for customers", "Customisation: The bag features a generous print area of 13 cm (W) x 25 cm (H), perfect for branding, logos, or promotional designs", "Colour: Available in a natural brown kraft paper colour, offering a rustic, environmentally conscious look."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31 cm W x 42 cm H x 11 cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Kraft", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4601l/ps4601l-kraft.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-brown-large-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
