  ('IntexGlobal','PS4602L','Kraft Paper Bag White Large Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-white-large-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4602l','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag White Large with Twisted Paper Handle—an elegant and eco-friendly packaging option perfect for your retail or promotional needs. This large kraft paper bag is designed to carry a variety of products while offering a clean and polished appearance.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 31 cm (W) x 42 cm (H) x 11 cm (G) — large enough to hold a wide range of products such as clothing, gifts, or home goods.", "Material: Made from 120gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is both biodegradable and recyclable, making it a sustainable alternative to plastic bags.", "Twisted Paper Handles: The bag includes durable twisted paper handles, ensuring a strong grip and ease of carrying for shoppers.", "Customisation: Personalise the bag with your logo or design using the 16 cm (W) x 16 cm (H) print area, making it perfect for promotional purposes.", "Colour: Available in a white finish, providing a clean, sophisticated backdrop for your branding."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31 cm W x 42 cm H x 11 cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4602l/ps4602l-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-white-large-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
