  ('IntexGlobal','PS4602LS','Kraft Paper Bag White Landscape Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-white-landscape-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4602ls','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag White Landscape with Twisted Paper Handle—an eco-friendly and stylish packaging solution designed to make a lasting impression. This landscape-shaped bag is perfect for retail use, promotional events, and more, offering both functionality and sustainability.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 42 cm (W) x 31 cm (H) x 11 cm (G) — spacious enough for a variety of products, from books and stationery to apparel and gifts.", "Material: Crafted from 120gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is biodegradable and recyclable, offering an environmentally conscious alternative to plastic bags.", "Twisted Paper Handles: The durable twisted paper handles provide a strong, comfortable grip for easy carrying.", "Customisation: Easily personalise the bag with your logo, message, or design using the 25 cm (W) x 13 cm (H) print area for a unique promotional impression.", "Colour: Available in a white finish, giving a clean, professional look that highlights your customisation."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "42 cm W x 31 cm H x 11 cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4602ls/ps4602ls-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-white-landscape-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
