  ('IntexGlobal','PS4602S','Kraft Paper Bag White Small Includes Twisted Paper Handle','kraft-paper-bag-white-small-includes-twisted-paper-handle-ps4602s','Bags','Paper Bags','Introducing the Kraft Paper Bag White Small with Twisted Paper Handle, a sleek and eco-friendly packaging solution for your retail or promotional needs. This compact and durable bag is perfect for small items such as cosmetics, accessories, and gifts.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 20 cm (W) x 29 cm (H) x 10 cm (G) — ideal for carrying small retail items or giveaways.", "Material: Made from 120gsm eco-friendly kraft paper, this bag is both biodegradable and recyclable, making it a sustainable choice for your brand.", "Twisted Paper Handles: The durable twisted paper handles ensure a secure and comfortable grip, perfect for carrying lightweight items.", "Customisation: The 9 cm (W) x 13 cm (H) print area allows you to showcase your logo, design, or message, creating a unique branding opportunity.", "Colour: Available in white, offering a clean, minimalist appearance that will make your customisation stand out."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "20 cm W x 29 cm H x 10 cm G"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4602s/ps4602s-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/kraft-paper-bag-white-small-includes-twisted-paper-handle/');
