  ('IntexGlobal','PS4811','5L Waterproof Dry Bag','5l-waterproof-dry-bag-ps4811','Bags','Tote Bags','Keep your belongings dry and secure with the Waterproof Dry Bag, designed to protect your items from water, dirt, and dust. Whether you''re kayaking, hiking, or traveling in wet conditions, this bag is an essential companion.',250,true,false,'["Dimensions: The bag measures 35.5 cm (H) x 28 cm (W), with a 5-litre capacity, providing ample space for essentials like phones, keys, and clothes while keeping them safe and dry.", "Material: Made of 210D nylon with a PVC lining, this bag is durable and water-resistant, offering protection against the elements.", "Roll Top Closure: The roll-top closure ensures a tight seal to keep water out, and it can be easily adjusted to secure the contents.", "Floats on Water: If accidentally dropped in water, the bag floats, keeping your items accessible and preventing them from sinking.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for activities such as kayaking, boating, camping, hiking, or any outdoor adventures where your gear needs protection from the elements.", "Easy Care: Spot clean and air dry for quick maintenance, ensuring your dry bag remains in top condition.", "Compact and Portable: Lightweight and easy to carry, making it convenient for travel and outdoor excursions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "35.5cm H x 28cm W"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4811/ps4811-black.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4811/ps4811-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps4811/ps4811-royal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.72,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/waterproof-dry-bag/');
