  ('IntexGlobal','PS500X18','Bondi Tritan Bottle With Stainless Base And Cap','bondi-tritan-bottle-with-stainless-base-and-cap-ps500x18','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','Stay refreshed in style with the Bondi Tritan Bottle with Stainless Base and Cap. This 740ml translucent bottle is designed for durability and convenience, featuring a sleek stainless steel base and lid, making it perfect for daily hydration on the go.',50,true,false,'["740ml Translucent Tritan Design: Lightweight, BPA-free, and shatter-resistant for everyday use.", "Stainless Steel Base and Cap: Provides added durability and a premium look.", "Leak-Free Lid: Secure, leak-proof design for spill-free use.", "Shatter and Stain Resistant: Built to last without compromising on style.", "Customizable for Branding: Ideal for rotary printing or engraving, with a shiny mirror finish for your logo or design.", "Eco-Friendly Packaging: Individually packed in a sustainable gift box, perfect for gifting or promotions.", "Care Instructions: Not suitable for carbonated or frozen liquids. Not recommended for hot liquids or dishwasher use."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "25cm H x 7cm Diameter"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Bk", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x18/ps500x18-bk.webp"}, {"name": "Bl", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x18/ps500x18-bl.webp"}, {"name": "Cl", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x18/ps500x18-cl.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x18/ps500x18-or.webp"}, {"name": "Rd", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps500x18/ps500x18-rd.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,fals