  ('IntexGlobal','PS500X55','Microfibre Sunglass / Phone Pouch Tech Accessory','microfibre-sunglass-phone-pouch-tech-accessory-ps500x55','Tech','Tech Accessories','Introducing the Microfibre Sunglass/Phone Pouch – a versatile, all-in-one solution for protecting and cleaning your sunglasses and mobile phone. This soft microfiber pouch offers a gentle yet effective way to keep your devices safe from scratches, dust, and smudges while on the go.',250,true,false,'["Microfiber Material: Soft and smooth, designed to protect both sunglasses and mobile phones from scratches and damage.", "Drawstring Closure: Secures your items in place, preventing accidental slips while offering easy access.", "Cleans and Protects: Doubles as a cleaning cloth to wipe away fingerprints, smudges, and dust from your sunglasses or phone screen.", "Compact and Convenient: Perfectly sized for most sunglasses and mobile phones, making it easy to carry in a bag or pocket.", "Durable Design: Built to withstand daily use, ensuring long-lasting protection for your devices."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9cm W x 18cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.03,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/microfibre-sunglass-phone-pouch/');
