  ('IntexGlobal','PS5102','Snazzy Custom Short Gripper Socks','snazzy-custom-short-gripper-socks-ps5102','Apparel','Socks','Designed for comfort and safety, our Snazzy Short Gripper Socks are the perfect blend of functionality and fashion, keeping you steady on any surface.',1,true,false,'["Soft and Cozy Material: Made from a premium blend of silicone and cotton, ensuring a comfortable fit for all-day wear.", "Enhanced Grip: Non-slip silicone patterns cover the entire sole, providing excellent traction on slick surfaces.", "Safety First: Ideal for daily use, offering stability and security on hardwood floors, tiles, and other smooth surfaces.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for lounging at home, practicing yoga, or engaging in physical activities.", "Stylish and Functional: Combines fashionable designs with practical features for everyday reliability."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "19 x 5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/custom-short-gripper-socks/');
