  ('IntexGlobal','PS8122','Neoprene Twin Wine Bottle Holder Cooler Bag','neoprene-twin-wine-bottle-holder-cooler-bag-ps8122','Bags','Cooler Bags','Introducing the Neoprene Twin Wine Bottle Holder, the perfect blend of style, functionality, and protection for your wine bottles. Whether you''re heading to a picnic, party, or on the go, this insulated holder ensures your bottles are transported with care.',250,true,false,'["Dimensions: Measures 24.5 cm (W) x 36.5 cm (H), providing ample space to securely hold two wine bottles.", "Material: Crafted from high-quality insulated neoprene, offering excellent protection from temperature changes while ensuring your bottles stay at the perfect temperature.", "Stitched Reinforcement: Features stitched reinforcement around the handles and opening for added durability and comfort while carrying.", "Separation Compartments: The holder is designed with separate compartments for each wine bottle, keeping them secure and preventing them from clinking together, reducing the risk of damage.", "Practical and Stylish: The sleek design offers both practicality and style, making it a great accessory for wine lovers.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for picnics, parties, gifts, or simply enjoying wine on the go."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "24.5cm W x 36.5cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8122/ps8122-black.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,4.57,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/neoprene-twin-wine-bottle-holder/');
