  ('IntexGlobal','PS8504','Sublimated Sports Towel','sublimated-sports-towel-ps8504','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Towels','Introducing our Sublimated Sports Towel, the perfect companion for workouts, outdoor activities, and intense sports sessions. Made from a high-quality nylon and polyester blend, this towel offers cooling relief with just a simple wet and wring action.',250,true,false,'["Durable Polyester Top: The 330gsm polyester top is perfect for vibrant sublimated designs, offering custom branding or logos.", "Soft Cotton Reverse: The 100% cotton reverse provides a soft, absorbent surface to wipe away sweat or moisture.", "Nylon and Polyester Blend: Designed for durability and flexibility, perfect for active use.", "Compact & Lightweight: Ideal for sports, fitness routines, outdoor activities, or even a day at the beach."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "100cm W x 40cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,6.35,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/?post_type=product&p=5167');
