  ('IntexGlobal','PS8504B','Sublimated Beach Towel','sublimated-beach-towel-ps8504b','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Towels','Introducing our Sublimated Beach Towel, the perfect combination of comfort, style, and durability. Crafted with a 330gsm polyester top and a 100% cotton reverse, this towel is designed to provide both vibrant custom prints and ultimate softness.',250,true,false,'["Premium Polyester Top: The 330gsm polyester top allows for vibrant, full-color sublimation prints, showcasing your unique designs or logos.", "Soft Cotton Reverse: The 100% cotton reverse offers a soft, absorbent surface for drying off after a swim or relaxing in the sun.", "Durable & Comfortable: Built for long-lasting use, ensuring comfort and style throughout the beach season.", "Customizable: Perfect for promotional events, branding, or personal use with full-color sublimation printing."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "150cm W x 75cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,9.35,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/?post_type=product&p=5168');
