  ('IntexGlobal','PS8510','Bondi Gym Cotton Towel','bondi-gym-cotton-towel-ps8510','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Towels','Introducing the Bondi Gym Cotton Towel, designed for maximum comfort and durability. Made from premium 400gsm cotton and featuring a polyester band, this towel is perfect for wiping away sweat and staying fresh during your workout sessions.',100,true,false,'["High-Quality 400gsm Cotton: Soft, absorbent, and gentle on the skin, perfect for gym sessions or outdoor activities.", "Durable Polyester Band: The polyester band adds strength and durability, ensuring the towel holds up through intense use.", "Ideal Size: Measures 40 x 75 cm, providing ample coverage for your workout or daily activities.", "Stylish and Practical Design: The strip size of 39 cm x 8 cm adds a modern, sleek look to the towel, making it a great accessory for your gym gear.", "Pet-Friendly Option: Perfect for pets, offering a comfortable and absorbent solution for bath or grooming time."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "40 x 75cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-royal-blue.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps8510/ps8510-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bondi-gym-cotton-towel/');
