  ('IntexGlobal','PS8774','Custom Air Fresheners Car Accessory','custom-air-fresheners-car-accessory-ps8774','Tools & Auto','Car Accessories','Introducing Custom Air Fresheners, these die-cut cardboard air fresheners are the perfect solution for a refreshing atmosphere, with a variety of scents to suit every preference.',1,true,false,'["Custom Design: Fully customizable die-cut cardboard shape to match your brand or personal style.", "Long-Lasting Freshness: Once opened, they stay fresh for approximately 7-10 days, and unopened, they last for up to 12 months.", "Convenient Packaging: Supplied individually wrapped for freshness and easy distribution.", "Variety of Scents: Choose from a range of popular fragrances including Jasmine, Rose, Ocean, Black Ice, and more."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "3cm x 3cm, 5cm x 5cm, 9cm x 9cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,null,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/custom-air-freshners/');
