  ('IntexGlobal','PS9107','Small Microfibre Cleaning Cloth Tech Accessory','small-microfibre-cleaning-cloth-tech-accessory-ps9107','Tech','Tech Accessories','Keep screens and lenses spotless while putting your brand in the spotlight with the Small Microfibre Cleaning Cloth. This practical and stylish accessory is a must-have for everyday cleaning needs.',250,true,false,'["High-Quality Material: Crafted from 230gsm microfibre, ensuring gentle, scratch-free cleaning for all surfaces.", "Versatile Use: Perfect for glasses, phone screens, computer monitors, camera lenses, and more.", "Full-Color Customization: Showcases your logo or design in vibrant and durable sublimation printing.", "Portable & Practical: Compact size fits easily in pockets, bags, or cases for on-the-go convenience.", "Eco-Friendly & Reusable: A durable and reusable alternative to disposable wipes, promoting sustainability.", "Perfect Brand Giveaway: A functional and attractive promotional item that clients and employees will appreciate."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "12cm x 12cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9107/ps9107-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.67,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/small-microfibre-cleaning-cloth/');
