  ('IntexGlobal','PS9202','Natural Lunch Box Home Decor','natural-lunch-box-home-decor-ps9202','Home & Living','Home Decor','Introducing our Natural Lunch Box, the perfect eco-friendly solution for your daily meals. Crafted from wheat straw, this lunch box is designed to reduce environmental impact while providing a practical and stylish way to store your food.',50,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Material: Made from wheat straw, a sustainable alternative to traditional plastics, reducing your environmental footprint.", "Bamboo Lid with Silicone Seal: The bamboo lid ensures a secure closure, keeping your food fresh and leak-proof.", "Sustainable Design: Not recommended for dishwashing to preserve the eco-friendly materials.", "Ideal Gift Option: Each lunch box is packed in an eco-friendly gift box, making it a thoughtful, sustainable gift choice."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "19.3 x 11.8 x 6.5 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9202/ps9202-black.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9202/ps9202-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/natural-lunch-box/');
