  ('IntexGlobal','PS9204','Set Of Four Measuring Spoons Home Decor','set-of-four-measuring-spoons-home-decor-ps9204','Home & Living','Home Decor','Introducing our Set of Four Measuring Spoons, a must-have kitchen tool for precise cooking and baking. Crafted from durable, food-safe materials, this set ensures accurate measurements for all your recipes.',100,true,false,'["Four Essential Sizes: Includes tablespoon, teaspoon, 1/2 teaspoon, and 1/4 teaspoon for versatile use in any recipe.", "Durable, Food-Safe Materials: Made from high-quality materials designed for long-lasting use.", "Conveniently Labeled: Each spoon is clearly labeled for easy identification, making measuring a breeze.", "Sturdy Handle: Features a comfortable grip for ease of use and control while measuring."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "17.8 x 3.2 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Silver", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9204/ps9204-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/set-of-four-measuring-spoons/');
