  ('IntexGlobal','PS9211','Swivel Nail Care Kit Grooming','swivel-nail-care-kit-grooming-ps9211','Personal Care','Grooming','Introducing the Swivel Nail Care Kit, a convenient and compact solution for all your nail grooming needs. This foldaway kit includes four essential nail files and buffers, designed to keep your nails smooth, shaped, and polished wherever you are.',50,true,false,'["Four Essential Tools: Includes a range of nail files and buffers to shape, smooth, and finish your nails with ease.", "Swivel Foldaway Design: Easy-to-store and travel-friendly design that keeps everything neatly organized and ready for use.", "Durable and Reliable: Crafted from high-quality materials for long-lasting, efficient nail care.", "Perfect for Home or Travel: The compact design makes it ideal for use at home, in your bag, or on-the-go."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "2.2 x 6.7 x 1.3 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Default", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/swivel-nail-care-kit/');
