  ('IntexGlobal','PS9220','Foldable Chair Cushion Home Decor','foldable-chair-cushion-home-decor-ps9220','Home & Living','Home Decor','Introducing our Foldable Chair Cushion, designed for added comfort and convenience. Made from durable polyester fabric with a foam interior, this cushion provides a comfortable seating experience wherever you go.',100,true,false,'["Foldable Design: Compact and easy to store, perfect for on-the-go use or for keeping in your car, at the park, or at outdoor events.", "Durable Polyester Fabric: Strong and long-lasting material that is easy to clean and maintain.", "Comfortable Foam Interior: Provides extra cushioning to enhance your seating comfort.", "Customizable Decoration: Features full-color transfer printing, allowing you to add vibrant designs or branding to the panels."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "30 (w) x 30 (h) x 3 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9220/ps9220-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9220/ps9220-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9220/ps9220-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/foldable-chair-cushion/');
