  ('IntexGlobal','PS9301','Bamboo Wireless Charger','bamboo-wireless-charger-ps9301','Tech','Wireless Chargers','The Bamboo Wireless Charger offers a sleek and eco-friendly solution for powering your devices, blending natural aesthetics with modern technology.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Design: Made from sustainable bamboo and durable ABS plastic for a modern, natural look.", "5W Wireless Charging: Compatible with any device that supports wireless charging, providing efficient and cable-free power.", "Certified Safe: CE, FCC, and ROHS certified for reliable and secure charging.", "Complete Package: Includes a USB-A to Micro USB cable for easy connection to laptops or USB wall sockets.", "Thoughtful Packaging: Packed in a stylish black paper gift box, ideal for gifting or promotional use.", "Specifications: Input 5V/1.5A; Output 5V/1.5A, delivering consistent performance."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "10(Dia) x 0.9(h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9301/ps9301-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/bamboo-wireless-charger/');
