  ('IntexGlobal','PS9403','4Pcs Wooden Cutlery Home Decor','4pcs-wooden-cutlery-home-decor-ps9403','Home & Living','Home Decor','Introducing our 4-Piece Wooden Cutlery Set, crafted from high-quality natural wood. This set offers an eco-friendly alternative to traditional cutlery, ideal for elevating your dining experience.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly Material: Made from high-quality, sustainable natural wood, offering a green alternative to plastic cutlery.", "Complete Set: Includes essential pieces – knife, fork, spoon, and a tissue paper – for a well-rounded dining experience.", "Smooth Finish: Each piece is meticulously crafted with smooth edges and a comfortable grip for ease of use.", "Versatile Design: Perfect for everyday meals, picnics, or special occasions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "21.5 x 6 cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Natural", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9403/ps9403-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/4pcs-wooden-cutlery/');
