  ('IntexGlobal','PS9451','Silicone Collapsible Pet Bowl Pet Accessory','silicone-collapsible-pet-bowl-pet-accessory-ps9451','Pet','Pet Accessories','Our Silicone Collapsible Pet Bowl is the perfect accessory for active pet owners who love to explore. Designed for ultimate convenience, this bowl offers both functionality and portability, ensuring your pet stays hydrated and fed during every adventure.',250,true,false,'["Durable Silicone Construction: Made from high-quality, flexible silicone that withstands daily use.", "Collapsible Design: Easily collapses to save space and expands when needed to hold food or water.", "Convenient Carabiner: Comes with a carabiner to clip the bowl to your leash, backpack, or belt loop for easy access and portability.", "Ideal for Travel and Outdoors: Perfect for walks, hikes, camping trips, or any outdoor activity with your pet."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "13cm W x 13cm L x 3cm H"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Light Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-light-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-red.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/ps9451/ps9451-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,2.02,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal