  ('IntexGlobal','PSBB03','Cromwell Tote Bag','cromwell-tote-bag-psbb03','Bags','Tote Bags','Introducing the Cromwell Tote Bag, a stylish and eco-friendly shopping companion designed with both functionality and sustainability in mind. The Cromwell Tote Bag features a biodegradable cardboard base that enhances durability while reducing environmental impact.',100,true,false,'["Dimensions: 36 cm W x 41 cm H x 11.5 cm D, providing ample space for your shopping and everyday essentials.", "Features Landtopia organic additive, tested in Australia (ASTM D5511-2012)", "Eco-Friendly Design: The tote bag is crafted with a biodegradable cardboard base, making it an excellent sustainable alternative to traditional bags.", "Material: Made from high-quality, durable materials for long-lasting use.", "Customizable: Easily customize the bag with your 25 cm W x 25 cm H image or design for a unique promotional or personal touch.", "Colour Options: Available in Black, Royal, and White, allowing you to choose the perfect style for your brand or needs.", "Convenient Use: The Cromwell Tote Bag is designed with convenience in mind, ideal for shopping, events, and everyday carry."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "36cm W x 41cm H x 11.5cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb03/psbb03-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb03/psbb03-blue.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb03/psbb03-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/cromwell-tote-bag/');
