  ('IntexGlobal','PSBB04','Zefa Biodegradable Tote Bag','zefa-biodegradable-tote-bag-psbb04','Bags','Tote Bags','The Zefa Tote Bag is an eco-friendly and durable choice, designed with both sustainability and practicality in mind. Crafted with a biodegradable non-woven material and featuring a cardboard base, this tote bag offers a large volume and structured design, making it perfect for various uses, including retail, trade shows, and more.',100,true,false,'["Eco-Friendly: Made from biodegradable non-woven material, offering a sustainable alternative to traditional bags.", "Features Landtopia organic additive, tested in Australia (ASTM D5511-2012)", "Dimensions: Generous size with ample space to carry essentials, making it ideal for shopping, events, and everyday use.", "Cardboard Base: Provides added structure and durability to the bag, ensuring it holds its shape and can carry more weight.", "Long Handle: Features a long handle for easy and comfortable carrying, making it convenient for users of all heights.", "Customizable: The large surface area is perfect for customizing with your logo or promotional design, making it a great option for branding and marketing purposes.", "Versatile Use: Ideal for retail, trade shows, events, and giveaways, combining style, practicality, and environmental consciousness."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "31cm W x 34cm H x 20cm D"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb04/psbb04-black.webp"}, {"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb04/psbb04-blue.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/psbb04/psbb04-white.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,false,null,5,'local_stock','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/zefa-biodegradable-tote-bag/');
