  ('IntexGlobal','SPBD31','2.2 Litre Gym bottle','2-2-litre-gym-bottle-spbd31','Drinkware','Drink Bottles','The 2.2 Litre Gym Bottle is a high-capacity, reusable water bottle, designed for fitness enthusiasts, athletes, and active lifestyles. Made from durable plastic, this bottle ensures ample hydration throughout workouts, sports, and daily activities.',250,true,false,'["2.2L Capacity: Perfect for keeping hydrated during intense workouts and long days.", "Durable Plastic Construction: Lightweight yet sturdy for everyday use.", "Ergonomic Handle: Easy to grip and carry, even during exercise.", "Leak-Proof Screw-On Lid: Prevents spills and ensures secure closure.", "Wide Mouth Opening: Easy to fill, clean, and add ice cubes or supplements.", "Ideal for Gyms & Outdoor Activities: Great for fitness, hiking, and sports events."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "10.6 in x 5.0 in (dia)"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/spbd31/spbd31-blue.webp"}, {"name": "Clear", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/spbd31/spbd31-clear.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/spbd31/spbd31-green.webp"}, {"name": "Pink", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/spbd31/spbd31-pink.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/spbd31/spbd31-red.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,4.08,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/2-2-litre-gym-bottle/');
