  ('IntexGlobal','STRS03','Football Stress Shape Stress Ball & Toy','football-stress-shape-stress-ball-toy-strs03','Toys & Games','Stress Balls & Toys','The Football Stress Shape is a great stress-relief tool designed to promote relaxation while showcasing your brand. Made from high-quality polyurethane foam, this football-shaped stress ball is lightweight, durable, and easy to squeeze, making it a perfect giveaway at sports events, promotional fairs, and corporate branding campaigns.',250,true,false,'["Football-Shaped Design: Ideal for sports-themed promotions and events.", "Helps Relieve Stress & Tension: Great for athletes, office workers, and event attendees.", "Compact & Lightweight: Easy to carry and store.", "Perfect for Sporting Events & Promotions: A unique and fun way to engage audiences."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "9.6 (w) x 6.3 (h) cm"}, {"name": "Durable Polyurethane Foam", "value": "Soft, squeezable, and long-lasting."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-red.webp"}, {"name": "White", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs03/strs03-white.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a462