  ('IntexGlobal','STRS14','Australia Stress Shape Stress Ball & Toy','australia-stress-shape-stress-ball-toy-strs14','Toys & Games','Stress Balls & Toys','The Australia Stress Shape is a fun and patriotic stress-relief item, designed to showcase national pride while promoting your brand. Made from high-quality polyurethane foam, this uniquely Australia-shaped stress ball is lightweight, durable, and easy to squeeze, making it a perfect giveaway for national events, tourism promotions, and corporate branding.',250,true,false,'["Australia-Shaped Design: A great way to celebrate national pride.", "Helps Relieve Stress & Tension: Ideal for offices, events, and giveaways.", "Available in Yellow & Customisable Colours: Can match brand or event themes.", "Compact & Lightweight: Easy to carry and store.", "Perfect for Promotional Events & Tourism Campaigns: A unique and engaging branding tool."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "11 (w) x 2 (h) x 9 (d) cm"}, {"name": "Durable Polyurethane Foam", "value": "Soft, squeezable, and long-lasting."}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/strs14/strs14-main.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.96,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/australia-stress-shape/');
