  ('IntexGlobal','STRS34','Oval Stress Shape Keyring Stress Ball & Toy','oval-stress-shape-keyring-stress-ball-toy-strs34','Toys & Games','Stress Balls & Toys','The Oval Stress Shape Keyring is a practical and stress-relieving promotional item, designed for convenience and everyday use. Made from high-quality polyurethane foam, this soft and squeezable stress ball comes with an attached keyring, allowing users to carry it effortlessly on bags, belts, or keys for instant stress relief wherever they go.',250,true,false,'["Durable Polyurethane Foam: Soft, lightweight, and squeezable for effective stress relief.", "Oval-Shaped Design: Comfortable to hold and easy to squeeze.", "Attached Keyring: Easily clips onto bags, belts, or keychains for portability.", "Compact & Convenient: Perfect for travel, office use, or daily carry.", "Great for Stress & Anxiety Relief: Ideal for busy professionals, students, and event attendees.", "Perfect for Corporate Giveaways & Promotions: A unique branding tool that keeps your business in customers'' hands."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "8 (w) x3 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Blue", "hex": "#0057B8", "image": ""}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "#FFD700", "image": ""}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "#FF6900", "image": ""}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "#C8102E", "image": ""}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "#009639", "image": ""}, {"name": "White", "hex": "#FFFFFF", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,0.37,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/oval-stress-shape-keyring/');
