  ('IntexGlobal','SUNG03','Wayferer Sunglasses','wayferer-sunglasses-sung03','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Sunglasses','Stay cool and protected with our <strong>Wayfarer Sunglasses</strong>, crafted from durable polycarbonate for a lightweight yet resilient frame. These timeless sunglasses are fitted with UV400 lenses that block 100% of harmful UVA and UVB rays, making them a stylish and practical choice for everyday wear or outdoor promotions. Whether you''re gearing up for a beach day, outdoor event, or corporate ',250,true,false,'["Durable polycarbonate frame for long-lasting wear.", "UV400 lenses block 100% UVA and UVB rays.", "Classic wayfarer design suits all face shapes.", "Lightweight and comfortable for extended use.", "Ideal for outdoor promotions, travel, and retail."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "15 (w) x 5 (h) x 14 (d) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Custom", "hex": "", "image": ""}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.21,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/wayferer-sunglasses/');
