  ('IntexGlobal','TRAV07','PU Leather Luggage Tag Travel Accessory','pu-leather-luggage-tag-travel-accessory-trav07','Travel','Travel Accessories','The PU Leather Luggage Tag is a sleek and functional travel accessory, crafted from soft PU leather material for a premium look and feel. Featuring an adjustable strap, this luggage tag is durable, secure, and ideal for identifying baggage while traveling. Perfect for corporate giveaways, airline promotions, and travel branding, it offers a stylish way to showcase your brand.',250,true,false,'["Soft PU Leather Material: Elegant, durable, and comfortable to the touch.", "Adjustable Strap: Ensures a secure fit on various luggage sizes.", "Window for Contact Details: Protects personal information while keeping it accessible.", "Lightweight & Travel-Friendly: Perfect for frequent travelers.", "Ideal for Suitcases, Backpacks & Travel Bags: Helps easily identify luggage."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "12 (w) x 8 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-green.webp"}, {"name": "Navy", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-navy.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-red.webp"}, {"name": "Yellow", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/trav07/trav07-yellow.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,1.05,28,'indent_sea'