  ('IntexGlobal','UMBR03','St Andrews Golf Umbrella','st-andrews-golf-umbrella-umbr03','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Umbrellas','Built to withstand the unpredictability of the outdoors, the St Andrews Golf Umbrella features durable materials, smart venting, and a reliable grip—making it the perfect companion on and off the course.',250,true,false,'["Equipped with a strong fibreglass shaft for lightweight durability.", "Double-vented canopy enhances wind resistance and sun protection.", "Sturdy non-slip handle ensures a secure, comfortable grip in any condition.", "Large coverage area ideal for golf, events, or everyday rain use.", "Stylish and practical—great for personal use or branded promotions."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "76 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr03/umbr03-green.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,9.56,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/st-andrews-golf-umbrella/');
