  ('IntexGlobal','UMBR04','Central Park Umbrella','central-park-umbrella-umbr04','Outdoor & Lifestyle','Umbrellas','The Central Park Umbrella combines style, convenience, and durability in a portable design. This 23-inch, 8-bone tri-fold automatic umbrella features a strong fibre-reinforced frame with a steel rod for added stability. Its 190T encrypted impact fabric provides reliable UPF 50+ sun protection, making it perfect for unpredictable weather. The comfortable plastic handle ensures a secure grip, while ',250,true,false,'["23-inch canopy with 8-bone structure.", "Tri-fold automatic opening for convenience.", "Fibre umbrella bones with steel rod for durability.", "190T encrypted impact fabric for weather resistance.", "UPF 50+ sun protection.", "Comfortable plastic handle."]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Size", "value": "43 (h) cm"}]'::jsonb,'[{"name": "Black", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr04/umbr04-black.webp"}, {"name": "Green", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr04/umbr04-green.webp"}, {"name": "Orange", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr04/umbr04-orange.webp"}, {"name": "Red", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr04/umbr04-red.webp"}, {"name": "Royal", "hex": "", "image": "https://pub-fbec7c9199f04af8ab95a413a4620d37.r2.dev/suppliers/intex/products/_variants/w400/umbr04/umbr04-royal.webp"}]'::jsonb,null,'supplier',true,true,7.34,28,'indent_sea','Intex','https://www.intexglobal.com/product/central-park-umbrella/');
